title: Pawmates: The Dog Meetup App
description:
Featured on 50+ news and media channels including BlogTO, Narcity, Newsweek, CTV, City News, Global News, Curiocity, and many more

Downloaded more than 50,000 times in 20+ countries

Pawmates is your friendly neighbourhood dog meetup app! Match, chat, and meet with dogs and their owners near you!

Find your pack! Looking to meet with like minded people who love their pets like you do? Look no further! Our matching works just like your favourite meetup apps. Swipe right on pups you like, left on those you don’t. Once you’ve matched with them, you can chat freely as much as you want, for free. We do NOT believe in pay to message (who wants to do that?)

Our features include:

CREATE YOUR CUSTOM PROFILE
Post photos of your pup, add details about them including their personality, age, breed, and more!

MATCH WITH PUPS
Unlimited free browsing of the cutest dogs in your area! Change your settings to specify the types of dogs and people you want to meet! Find your gang!

CHAT AND MEET
Pawmates matches show up on your custom wheel! Swipe through your match wheel and start chatting with people and their pups!
Connect with pups near you by organizing meet ups!

OUR PET BUSINESS MAP

Looking for the top rated vets, pet food stores, walkers, or anything else related to your pup like the best park in your area? Hop on over to our Pawmates Map and check out every animal business in your area!

Pawmates is here not only to help you meet your new dogpack, but to help with every other need of pet owners and we're growing daily! We want to build the biggest community of dog lovers around the world. So come join our family today!

CONTACT US!
Have questions, problems, or feedback? Feel free to contact us @ Pawmatesapp@gmail.com Or visit us at our Instagram and Facebook pages to win amazing prizes and giveaways!

YOUR PRIVACY IS IMPORTANT TO US
Please read the terms and policies of Pawmates, as well as the privacy policy carefully. All data is handled under the terms and policies of Pawmates privacy policy. More details can be found here: https://pawmatesapp.com/terms-of-service/

comments: ['Great app and presents well visually but always fails to send Notifications when receiving chat messages forcing you to manually check in on conversations.', 'Decent app, but would be more effective with more members- obviously not the fault of the developer, but still a shortcoming. Adding the option to delete chats would be good.', "12 people are within my 50 mile radius. 7 of those people want to breed their dogs. 2 of those people want to date. And another 1 just wants a pet sitter. This app isnt regulated Edit: I did attempt to report these profiles. There wasn't a report option. Or it's incredibly difficult to find. Either or.", "Won't use proper location. Locks when I try to update the location. Won't let me delete account.", 'Fantastic app loved all the people', 'Very user friendly app. A lot of great matches for my little Barky. Me and 🐕 really loving this app.', "I love pawmates but they are the same dog s and no one manage me back but it's still a good app", 'This is a great way to meet other pets. 5/5!!', 'Great app my dog loves it']

title: DogDater
description:
Few animals are as social as our dog friends, yet no social App is devoted to THEIR needs for daily quality interactions until now! DogDater is an app created by dog lovers for dog lovers to help your dog flourish and find new friends. It allows you to follow and meet other dogs around the world regardless of where they are and based on your personal preferences such as breed, characteristics, and gender. 
The App includes lots of functions that will make your and your dog’s life happier: The yard allows you to stay up to date on what your favorite dogs are doing. You can also showcase your dog's life and news about it. You can create and join groups in your area or based on your dog's interests. This is a great way to connect with more dogs and to share tips and thoughts about your and others' dogs. You can also send direct messages to other dog owners and meet up, or recommend nice dog places, exciting parks, or any favorite dog accessories your dog might want to share with their friends. The App also makes it easy for you to keep track of your dog's family history, and find your dog's long-lost brothers and sisters.
We have just launched the App and are planning to add lots of exciting functions very soon, such as a marketplace, online courses, dog psychology, dog walking, dog sitting, parking, mating, and pedigrees for breeding all over the world. Welcome to DogDater The world's best community for dogs!
summary: The App for all dog lovers. Find dogs around the world & around the corner.

comments: ["The only people that are popping up for me are swedish, not a single person from any where else, I'm not sure if this is because of the only people on this app are living in Sweden or I've set something up wrong or this app has messed up, anyways would be great if people were more local", "Not really usable for me without the option to search in a specific area in the city. I'm not gonna commute with my two dogs, one of them with arthritis, to meet another dog. I understand it might work for other people, but it is a very simple feature to add an address to the account information and be able to search based on that. You basically already have that with the city...", 'Fantastic app. Really been waiting for an app like this. Thank you for making it happen!']

title: Rexi - Dog lovers dating app
description:
Have you been swiping left and right for finding your match? After you finally met your love, you suddenly discovered that your ideal match does not love dogs at all!
Don't waste your time: finding a partner who loves dogs as much as you do became easier with our app!  Discover someone who would appreciate puppy kisses and wagging tails!
🐕 Rexi will show you nearest dog lovers. "Like" or "pass" on each dog lover you see. After you press like they'll be notified directly. If there's mutual interest, you'll be matched so you can begin chatting about all things puppies. 
We know that life is better with dogs, and we want to share it with someone who feels the same. If you know your soul mate is out there and loves dogs the way you do, give us a try! 🐶
For questions & cooperation drop a message: support@rexi.app
summary: Connect worldwide dog lovers for friendship, romance, doggy play or just fun!
developerAddress: Armenia, Yerevan, 0031

title: Dating App Marry Me - Singles
description:
Are you looking for a partner?

Do you think it’s impossible to get to know someone online the same way you can in real life? 
Have you yet to find the right platform for reputable matchmaking?

Then Marry Me is the perfect place for you!

Writing love letters before seeing the recipient? It works differently in real life! That’s why Marry Me is also different!

Marry Me works just like real-life dating: catching a glimpse, being charmed, making contact

•	Do you want to make your decision using visual criteria and is your partner’s appearance extremely important to you? Then simply adjust the app settings to search and find your favourites based on appearance. 
•	Are your partner’s personality traits important to you? Then use our tag (keyword) search filter. This allows you to meet partners worldwide who meet your specified criteria. 
•	Are you looking for someone within a specific radius, in another city or even in another country? Then enter your preferred location in the radius search to further refine this based on tags.
•	Do you want to show someone that you’re genuinely interested in them and stand out from the crowd? Then send them a gift, such as a virtual rose with your own personal greeting, for example. 

If you’re seeking a user-friendly dating app with a large community of single men and women, download Marry Me now, free of charge.

Marry Me will help you find and date potential partners. This online dating app allows you to find your partner based on your own criteria and arrange proper dates.

Use the Marry Me dating app to quickly and easily find and meet singles nearby or around the world. 
  
The high-quality graphics, complex search algorithm, smart matchmaking engine, matching game, radar function for finding people nearby and the option to use the tag filter to search for matches will make this online dating app your first port of call.
 
Why should I install this online dating app?
 
1. Marry Me includes a radar function that allows you to only be notified of singles who are located within a specific radius of you. This feature is the perfect choice for all those who are not interested in long-distance relationships.
 
2. This online dating app contains a large database of single men and women to ensure that there are always a few matches for you.
 
3. Unlike other dating apps, where you have to perform rather complex steps in order to chat with other people, this dating app makes it very easy to flirt with local singles and talk about anything you want.
 
4. So that you can get to know new people and meet local singles, this dating app has a powerful, intelligent matchmaking engine that allows you to find single men and women with whom you have much in common.
 
And because you can download and test this dating app free of charge, why not give it a try and experience the features for yourself?
 
Marry Me at a glance:
 
•	Clear, modern design with a fresh, intuitive interface
•	High-quality graphics with smooth navigation
•	Intelligent matchmaking engine that helps you find a partner
•	Find local singles nearby or worldwide (based on the specified radius)
•	Flirt and chat with strangers
•	Meet new people all over the world
•	A large community of men and women with different interests
 
Download the Marry Me online dating app free of charge to meet local or international singles. Complete your profile and browse available singles near your current location or around the world.

comments: ["I created a log in with my email and a password, I never got the email to verify the account and haven't been able to log in.... I'm not sure if this app is just accumulating/stealing emails and passwords...seems like I'm not the only one after reading reviews.", "Its so very plain. Kind of like speed dating. Very vague. Tiny pictures, tiny profiles. Theres no real direction. And plain white bright background. I ts like it's missing its personality. I expected WAY better for a marriage app. 👎", "Great app!!! But too many ads. The admin should work on this challenge. But if you are having issues with your partner cheating on you, contact mojohacker7gmailcom, the agency will help you remotely access your partner's phone and all phone calls and incoming messages will be seen on both sides.", "Feels pretty bad to spend all this time doing the questionnaire and setting up my profile just for the app not to work, won't and people in my area and I have tried changing my search preference and just says error would not recommend get this app.", "Nice application but offer 24hours free trial and unable to message anyone this is so disappointing, this can be deemed as FALSE ADVERTISING, clearly you don't understand the concept of free trial should include messages even if it's a minimum of let's say 15 or 20 allowed within the 24 hours free trial 😉 come on this way people would be willing to subscribe if they like the application 😀 please do something about this", "dont waste your time,fake photo's and profiles and i set my location to london uk and its showing women from over seas,all too often there are always women from over seas rather then here in the uk.this app would be good but changes need to be made.", 'I keep seeing "connecting to chat please wait and repeat" on my screen when I try to reply or send messages. Please resolve this as soon as possible', 'It is a very good dating app.I like it because it is fast and efficient.Ads are minimal I will recommend anyone looking for a love partner instantly.Definitely a five star review.', "I don't know what happen to this app network is too slow for pictures,messages and for other things. This app need network please check and reset the network", "Your app is faulty it says I am a member which I've never signed up and yet it says my email is already token and yet I'm the owner of it and I never signed it until today and can't because it's not working", 'Terrible all fake profiles of less then classy women. This app screams money grab. I hate signing up and giving my information. Just to have wasted my time. These dating apps are wretched.', 'Very bad app you can not even send messages.. if you can not get the premium subscription do not bother downloading it', "It's a horrible app. I never made it past the sign in. It just keeps loading and loading.", 'This is worst app I have ever seen in my life..... I keep on creating my profile and it will not allow me in the web.... I guess this app is just using a network jamming to get money.', "Within 5 minutes of signing up on this app, I got a match amd I've met nice people on this app so far. This is a great app guys.", "It's very bad app the moment I receive massages from my matches you say connection fail and then ,u ask for payment y can't you just be like other app your going to loose alot off users👿😤👎👎👎👎👎👎👎👎👎", 'Perfect app and very simple and have a nice people on it And you can date easily i recommend it to everyone want date nice person', "Since yesterday that I installed this app it just keep on stopping on my phone, I'll be deleting my account soon if it doesn't stop today .", "The most stupid dumpest app..am new here and I was given a premium if 24hrs but I can't even send messages.. absolutely stupid app ever", "It's not showing girls of my region till month and many more problems. Overall it's totally fake app", 'The worst app ever , everything is slow and always showing error.', "Messaging doesn't work, most of not all women on this app are spam.", 'Fake app I completed all settings then after filling all they told me that there is technical problem. I hate🤨', 'Is a good app....but the problem about is... connection to chat wait to repeat... please please please you people should do something about it.. before people will be deleting app from their phones..thank you', "You can't text anyone there's no button for texting someone which is bad", "This app is error, I can't send message is showing me Connection failed", "Why can't i reply messages to the people who are texting me...once i reply a text am told that connection to chats but no", "This I cant chat with other people I hate this app alot because we can't chat 😡😡 if u can make it properly thank u for app", "Hello dear that app is awesome but I can't message if it be possible solve that problem thanks", 'Tried to open matches tab and it crashes.', "Anyway, I'm new to this app right now. So I just don't know much about it. But I just have been experiencing something here actually I hate that:/. Why I can't able to exit?😒", 'Very bad website takes very long to send a text', "If there's zero star I would have rate this app zero. title: NticeMe Dating
description:
NticeMe is the ultimate dating app for finding love and meeting new, interesting people. 

Whether you're looking for a partner, a lover, or just someone to chat with, NticeMe is the right app for you. Thousands of women and men are waiting to match with you. 

On NticeMe, it's easy to find love and start new relationships. 

Skim through thousands of profiles of people who have similar interests, check out their info and images, and like the ones that you find intriguing. Get matched and start chatting. Long-lasting relationships are just around the corner.

Sign up now, set up your profile, and start looking for dates. Find a match in no time!


BECOME A DATE CATCHER

Subscribe to “Date Catcher” to gain access to the premium features. Get unlimited likes to increase your matching chances and more. Always be in the primary inbox when you message someone. In short, you can become a VIP within seconds. And we promise you that subscribers will get the special treatment they deserve. Subscribe now and get matched more often. 

----- 

The subscription prices vary by age and country. You are always able to see the precise subscription price in the app. When you are subscribed, your card will be charged automatically to renew your subscription. You can deactivate your subscription at any time, as long as it is 24 hours before the end of your current subscription period.  

You can find our Privacy Policy and Terms of Use below: 

https://www.nticeme.app/terms-of-service 

https://www.nticeme.app/privacy

title: Fetchadate
description:
FetchaDate is Where Pet Lovers Meet! The place to connect for friends, pet playdates, and especially a date for you!

DATING, FRIENDS, PET PLAYDATES
What we do at FetchaDate is eliminate the hurdle to who you’re looking for. We are the dating app where singles meet over what they already love: dogs, cats, and maybe even exotic pets.

Those who trust FetchaDate are people who treat their pets as family so you don’t have to worry about them not being a “pet person”. Now, we can’t guarantee every person on here loves animals, but chances are they wouldn’t be here if they didn’t.

NO PET, NO PROBLEM
We understand people may be between pets at the moment so ‘No Pet, No Problem!’ Choose from a variety of virtual pets that represent your lifestyle like a bird, fish, turtle, horse, pig, or even a snake!

HERE’S HOW IT WORKS - YOU GET A WINGPET!
You can tell a lot about a person through their pet and that helps make better matches. With FetchaDate, your “WingPet” starts things off making your introduction. Your pet’s picture is seen first, and your pet gives clues about your interests. Why is the pet seen first? We feel this leads to more success, because who wouldn’t swipe right on a cute pet? And, Fetchadate creates a better experience by bonding over common ground.

CHANGING THE RULES TO FIND YOUR MATCH
Searching offers a few options:

1. See a pet you like and swipe right. And, if their owner swipes right on you, find them in your “Matches” tab. Swiped right but not a match yet? They will appear in your “fav’d” tab.
OR
2. See a pet and scroll up to get clues about the owner before swiping left or right.
OR
3. Need to see the person before swiping? Tap on the ? to see who’s behind that pet and select a heart for yes or X to keep fetching.

PROFILES: FETCH - MATCH - DATE
In FetchaDate, it’s quick to create your free profile including your values, interests, and personality. A profile also consists of name, age, location, occupation, and motto. And, you get to make a profile for your real or virtual pet.

FREE TO USE PLUS UPGRADES
FetchaDate is free to download, and create a profile with a limit on swipes, and chat!
We offer optional in-app purchases of monthly, 6 months, and 1 year subscriptions with discounts available. Subscriptions offer boosts, extended swiping, chat, and additional pet profiles. Price chart is displayed in the app before making a purchase.

Any free trial period is for a limited time. Any unused portion of a free trial period is forfeited after purchasing a subscription.

Payment will be charged to your Google Play account after purchase confirmation. Your subscription will automatically renew for the same term and price. You may cancel your subscription up to 24 hours before the next billing cycle.

You can manage your subscription in your phone’s account settings.
If you don’t choose to purchase a subscription, you may continue fetching on FetchaDate for free with limitations.

FOUNDER
Sheryl Matthys is the bestselling author of Leashes and Lovers: What Your Dog Can Teach You About Love, Life, and Happiness. From the moment Sheryl got her first Greyhound, people on the streets of NYC started talking to her. Right then she knew the secret to dating, friendships, and love! Sheryl’s appeared on ABC World News, Animal Planet, BRAVO, E!, Fox & Friends, The New York Times and more.

TERMS AND PRIVACY
Fetch on FetchaDate worry free. Check out our terms and privacy policy.
Terms of Use: https://fetchadate.com/terms/
Privacy Policy: https://fetchadate.com/privacy-policy

comments: ['Not enough users. I set my radius for around 30 miles, got one profile that I was not interested in, then no one else. Expanded my radius to around 50 miles, got one profile I accidentally swiped left on, then profiles have shown up since.', "Cool App! I love dogs and animals! If you're looking for someone, this would be a good place to find someone with similar interests.", 'This is a cute, easy to use app. I would definitely be using it if I were single, will refer my son to it.', "Great app...great idea....even linked up from Australia.....and it's inclusive of my three mates, my two staffies and my lorikeet", '"Unexpected error occurred" EVERY time I enter my phone number to open the app...🤨👎', "Doesn't work, after I type in my phone number press next. It will not complete the action.", "Can't even open app. Keeps shutting down.", "I thought this would be Great idea because I love dogs and would love to meet someone with the same passion, but it's not accepting my phone number. It doesn't let me go any further. Anyone that can help me?", 'I like the concept. But what about other pets besides Dogs and Cats? What about Birds and Reptiles lovers?', 'It is a very easy and useful app to use', "It's and interesting take on dating but truth is if my dog don't like ya I won't either", 'Pretty cute concept', 'Not many close options in Ct', "It doesn't work", 'Finally an app for me.', '𝓕𝓮𝓽𝓬𝓱𝓪𝓭𝓪𝓽𝓪 𝓘𝓼 𝓣𝓱𝓮 𝓑', 'Seems cool', 'Wow wow', 'Gg']

title: SinglesAroundMe - GPS Dating
description:
At SinglesAroundMe (our nickname is SAM), our focus has always been on building a great local dating app that helps you locate and connect with nearby singles.  Since our initial launch as the world's first location-based GPS dating app in 2010, we have grown our company, evolved the platform and have connected millions of local singles together around the globe, bringing hope, love and opportunity to so many. 

During this period of unprecedented anxiety and social upheaval, we want to help in every way we can. We are concerned not only for the people who we work with, who remain fully-employed, but also about social isolation and the mental health of isolated people globally, as social distancing stretches into the future. 

To this end, we have included access to our featured "Destination" search service as part of our basic free membership to allow you to meet people beyond 100 miles (160KM) and all around the world, even if you can't travel there right now. We also are also providing free access to "My Likes” so you can circle back to people you have "Liked" and would like to connect with. Now you can send them a message or nudge to hopefully match, providing you with a second chance to make a first impression!

Spread the word, build the community and offer one another the gift of human connection at a time when we could all benefit from a hug.

My name is Chris Klotz and I created the SinglesAroundMe dating app for people like you. I met my wife by chance while on the the University of Cambridge ski team in the French Alps and I know that these kinds of chance encounters can lead to great happiness, love and wild romance. I also know there is a bit of luck needed in meeting and dating like-minded singles and I hope that SinglesAroundMe can serendipitously help you to discover and meet someone special that is nearby.

Here are just some of our cool features:

★ 100% Free to join and discover local singles. Easy registration with Facebook or quickly by form. 

★ AroundMe: Swipe through profiles of nearby singles and engage with people that interest you.

★ GPS verified users are displayed as “heart pins” on our patent pending privacy protected  “Check In Location” interactive map.

★ byChance: Meet people you crossed paths with throughout your day.

★ Mingle Room: Presents the newest and most active members in your area to one another.  

★ Like" or “Dislike" photos and keep a fresh list of all the users you “Like”.

★ See who has already “Liked” your profile. 

★ Users that match (mutually "Like" each other) can talk for free.

★ Travelling for work or pleasure beyond your current location? Use the "Destination Search" tool to meet new and interesting people wherever you plan on going. 

★ Message anyone that interests you and let your personality shine through. 

★ Keep track of all conversations in the message section.

★ Check "New Users" that have recently joined in your area.
 
★ 100% location-based, 100% GPS dating.

★ Location Privacy: Choose when to "show", "hide" or "shift" your location on the Last Check-In map. 

★ The last Check-In location gives you the opportunity to verify that the person you're chatting with is really where they say they are and not someone faking it. 

★ Control how you wish to receive messages by email or app notification or both.

Nudity is strictly prohibited and users can monitor and report any bad behaviour. 

On Valentine's Day, SinglesAroundMe was featured on the cover of the USA Today and on ABC World News Tonight as one of the world's leading dating apps.

From New York to Los Angeles, London to Sydney, Vancouver to Toronto and on college and university campus 's around the world, the SAM app is spreading wildly.

Upgrade to SinglesAroundMe Plus for unlimited daily messaging and to see who has Liked you and so much more. 

Please send us feedback or ask questions directly at customerservice@singlesaroundme.com.

comments: ['So barely started to use, so far , like the options of features and the layout of the UI dashboard and etc. It does have potential, but when I go into the "around me" , it does not load the map fully so I cant see whose around me or not. Just a greyish background , but everything else loads on the screen. So I can\'t fully explore and and see how the "around me" part works, but if you go to the " faces" tab , then you\'ll see a list. Which it\'s not bad, Simple, easy to navigate. To continue.', 'Scam. I feel I have been stolen after having paid for the premium feature. I am looking for friends around the world but the so-called travel feature just won\'t be able to find places such as \'New York\' or \'London\', let alone cities around my State. "No such location". Yeah... The developers might live in a different planet, who knows. No wonder the very few people I did find around me have last logged in around 2012, 2015 at best.', "I just honestly started using it so we will see what happens if anything at all I will rate again in about a month. As of yet I have not had any problems with the app it's easy to use, the layout is simple and it's free. Not hardly any ads which is a very nice feature like a lot of people theses days I'm on limited income so can't afford some of these subscriptions to these sites and so the free ones is where I be going all the time but the ads make me stop using them.", "Had it less than 24 hours and it won't stop bugging me to rate it. Kept it a couple of weeks. Delete Every single person I spoke with on this app was a verifiably fake profile. Many thought they were sneaky by being able to show the profile was in a particular place but then later noticing they were actually in Africa. One person even started to talk to me using their native language. It never did stop bugging me to rate it. Even after I had. The ones that seem real the app required membership.", "This is loaded with bugs for me. I got to the login page once after making an account. Not even an hour and 8% battery loss. Won't load any photos I take. Pics of others don't show including the profile pic. If nothing works in 2 days I'll just uninstall the app. I don't recommend paying for anything on this app. It's been around since 2012 and acts like it's still in hardcore development", "it's a great app oh, it seems like it's free to talk to people. It's a little bit awkward when you find out that there's somebody single right down your block. So people aren't necessarily putting their best picture out there. unfortunately, there are scammers out there and it's hard to tell if somebody really likes you or they're just trying to take advantage of you. yes there are fake females out there.", "It's really tough getting a proper feel for an app when it only opens once every 20 or so tries. Or after you finally uninstall, restart, reinstall, and open the app... Or when you can't navigate properly through the app... Or when you can't see any photos of anyone.", 'ok so who ever manages the app, needs to pay more attention to what profile your putting with the pictures. you have 3 of the 4 likes, all the same profile, but different pictures. you might want to fix this. im not real happy with the overall app or experience. oh and a key point here, that is not shared by the developer is, you have to wink or like someone in order to talk to them.... and ive only had the app, and 2 scammers have hit me up. this is a common thing, but doesnt have to be.', 'The app is great but the check in location messages and who checked you out should be free because it says everything free on the app when you look at it. And where they are from should tell you where they are from like county city and town because sometimes it just says England and not where from in England. It also keeps saying that I carnt register and email address is already in use and registration error It told me to email you apart from those few things it was a really good app thanks Lee', 'I have tried many times to register on this app. Always gives an error "there\'s an error with your gps coordinates". What a waste of time. I use a new phone with Android 9.1 on it and all my other apps work perfectly. What a waste of time', 'Subpar at best you cant really do much with out a subscription. There should be a free trial or some kind of messaging to get the full experience of this app. This app does have great potential but with the limited access make it very difficult to meet people on this app', 'Very poor the app never opens or displays any pictures of people or my profile for that matter cant chat to anyone or basically do anything without paying for it why would anyone pay for something they can even use on the basics. If I could have gave it zero stars I would have i think the idea about it is good but it needs to work first.', "Been checking it out for quite a while now, and it is nothing but bots. Scams. I've been around plenty of apps, and aside from you cant do anything unless you pay a subscription fee, all anyone who messages says is the EXACT same scam message. (There is no way 27 women all say the exact same serious relationship message everytime in the same way) which is too bad. otherwise the app seems to have potential, just expensive and I am especially not paying if all I see is the same scam artistry.", "Only really just started using it. Any reviews other than mine might do better for someone. As I'm already semi invested in one, I don't prefer to spend $20+ per app. I might give this a second review and give it 5 🌟's after a while. For now I'll leave it where it's at 3 seems fitting. I may very well delete, (SAM) is a nice concept with poor/horrible execution. 🙊", "Instead of paying money for upgrades, only able to link up with nobody because I am the only person in my nation on it... join a group on Facebook titled : Single Friends,USA. It has 50 state subgroups. It's totally free. The profiles are verified. Post an activity and get singles related conversation there.", 'used to be free to contact other members. now costs money. loaded with fake users. had 2 messages and 4 winks after signing up. they all looked fake. and none were in my area. can no longer message without paying. used to be 100% free. not a lot of users in my area. there are free alternatives with larger user base.', "i downloaded the app just see how it is. disappointed. members around me, well lets just say im years late. All old profiles and not even on line anymore. Even seen a 14 years on here with a profile. like really, wow. you definitely need to relaunch a new version and start over. If you don't wont to go to prison for talking on this app,, then dont download it. underage kids, thats right kids have profiles on here.", "I signed up. The next day can't get on. Keep getting error message. The server sent back something not understood. I tried emailing customer support twice no response. So I am deleting the app. I can't use it.", "Only been on here less than a day and you want a review..OK. so far the only problem I have is that it had my account still open from the last time I had this app so I already had my profile filled out. All of sudden its gone and says I need to have one..tried but it won't let me! Frustating to say the least! Please fix!", 'Registering is easy until you have to enter your location, it never picks up location and only say " error " without location, registration process can not be completed!! No use in sending them an email, they never respond! WON\'T RECOMMEND THIS APP!!!!!', "I find this apt terrible, freezes continuously, won't let you update information such as address or photo.. Or certainly wouldn't me, I uninstalled and reinstalled several times, says I've likes and messages but upon checking.. Nothing.. Glad it's free because I wouldn't pay for this garbage.. Totally unimpressed.", "I can't even load a location making a new account ,I factory reset 2 devices ,uninstalled, reinstalled ,the app just needs to be improved ,or there network needs improvment , buffering of pictures not loading I'm using the latest version of the app and another device now ,and I factory reset both devices so there fresh no doubt ,the app needs work and a lot of fine tuning ,,and a lot of fake profiles,that's just my honest opinion ,,I'm defeated ,I'm a grade 17 ntwk egnr largest telecom usa", "I've delete the app because it wont even open and show one person, the searching location just turns the whole time. Very disappointing. I never even got to see one face and i tried reinstalling it...... same thing happened.", "Im having problems with being able to send messages to respond to conversations. When you click on send it just continues to say load but isn't doing anything. It's like the app has frozen", "I downloaded it with pleasure. I tried to register. But on getting go where I should select country, it did not respond. I clicked register, it says country is required. I tried to select country again it didn't work too. The builder wasted his time in creating an app that cannot be used. And I wasted my megabite in downloading. Why should google play store include an app that's not working properly? Google can improve its store reputation by including only working app", "I love the fact that you can view singles that's literally less than 5 miles away from you you can basically see their whole location face and profile and what they're looking for the only thing that's missing is a live option I wish we could go live on this app that will put the icing on the cake other than that I love the app", "Practically you can't search within any distance even if you try to search locally. NO ONE checks out your profile even if you did not hide it. Since this app gives you no value whatsoever, it does not even make sense to use it as a paid VIP member. App is a total waste of times disallowing you to even edit or delete your profile. This should get a zero star even.", 'Its not uncommon for a dating app to have features locked behind a paywall, yet this one failed almost immediately as soon as I got a message from another user, it required me to subscribe to that paywall. For those who are single and want to save their money, use something other than this app.', 'Cheer 💘 anyone tested this app? Why there is such hemorrhoids with a bunch of ads and a lot of bots? 😒 App is so-so, as far as I caught, this is just a unmodified copy of the original site likevirt point com, only likevirt has a bunch of real profiles, bonuses for newbies and also there is weight gifts 🎁. Just for the pleasure register, see the profiles, photos! If you have liked keep liking it! 👍💪', "Good idea to show who's on the map where you choose by satellite view which I feel me and others would prefer but nobody wants to pay to socialize with people. If this app was free it could see off all the competition literally with the satellite view.", "App is a bit glitchy. It no longer shows photos and every once in a while I have to uninstall and reinstall the app for it to work. Have had some chats on here but haven't met anyone in real life on here yet.", 'NONE of the people who contacted me were even in my state. So if "around me" means the same country, this is a great app. If you want someone within, say, even 100 miles of you, try another app, unless you live in a big city on the east coast in which case you might stand a chance.', "This app looks great, but there isn't enough single Sydney women on it, it shows you all the single and looking for someone girls/guy's, either in your immediate location or right out to global, if more people used this app it would be so cool and so easy to almost instantly organize a date with whatever type of person you feel like on any given occasion, I work hard and haven't got alot time to go out and chase women the old fashion way, so EVERYONE PLEASE GET THIS APP AND START SHARING THE LOVE", 'Every 3 minuted its asking me to rate. Stop!!!! Ill rate after ive actually had a chance to use the damn thing without a pop up popping up to ask me to rate! For crying out loud man. Worse than a 2 year old asking why. I just lowered it again to 1* because even aftere i rated it. Its still asking me to rate it. I literally just paid for the sub. And im about to call and cancel and ask for my money back. Havent even owned it a full day', "I was an early user of this app and though i never met anybody with it i thought it had potential. I cancelled and stopped using this app at least 2 years ago, cut to now. I decide to give the app another try so i install it on my phone and start registration when i finish i'm notified email already in use. Contact cs every day for 4+ days no response nothing, what i really dont get is why my address is in use if i quit 2 years ago. Doesnt sound good to me.", "This app is a scam! Iook at every selfie and u can see there taken professionally by someone else! The model isn't even looking at the phone!I have messaged over 200 woman, some even wanting rose's! And I told them I had extra rose's, and not one reply! So I call it steeling our money!", 'Cheer 💘 who checked this dating app? Why there is such a problem with constant advertising? 😓 Dating app is so-so, as far as I understood, this is just a unmodified copy of the popular site likevirt point com, only likevirt has a bunch of real profiles, a large selection of partners and also there is weight gifts 💝❤️. Just for the pleasure sign in, have fun😍💋! If you tested keep liking it! 👍💪', 'I get messages from "women" (could be bots for all I know), but it requires a subscription to reply to them. Hot garbage. If the free product is trash, nobody will use it, and the product will be useless. Don\'t waste your time.', "It would not let me delete my profile. There was no delete profile button. I did not subscribe for that reason. Further, when I went to subscribe screens said pmt by the year 99.00 instead of by month as advertised. Unhonorable, probability of little more than phishing scam + other nefarious intents. Pictures of pretty girls are free & I won't pay to be lied to.", 'I have been approached by more scammers than any other dating app. Reported one to the site admin and that profile is still on there. I have not yet been approached by a legitimate female looking for a relationship. Other than that the site is easy to use and navigate.']

title: Dogo — Puppy and Dog Training
description: Dogo App is a positive dog training app with more than 4.000.000 parents and their 5.000.000 happy dogs. Dogo helps dog parents to train their dogs at home and build a stronger relationship, and you will have tools such as dog clicker & puppy whistle to support the puppy & dog training. Dogo is revolutionizing puppy and dog training. The app offers professionally tailored programs for dog parents that are curated by experienced dog trainers and veterinarians. Users can also exchange their experiences with other dog parents and share videos of their pets. In addition, your smart pet will learn obedience with our Dog Clicker! WITH DOGO APP YOU CAN ★ Choose what to teach your pup from the library of +100 dog tricks with video instructions. ★ Ask help & talk with real dog trainers professionals. ★ Send a training video to the Dogo trainer and get personal feedback on your dog’s performance. ★ Use our built-in dog clicker or puppy whistle to mark a behavior, the precise moment for which your doggo is rewarded, and reduce puppy training time. ★ Read our knowledge-based articles about dog obedience training, puppy behavior, nutrition, and health. ★ Pass personalized training programs for your puppy. WHY USE DOGO APP? ★ Train a dog or puppy: teach important skills with the dog clicker. ★ Solve behavior issues: say goodbye to barking, chewing, biting, etc. ★ Try +100 guided dog training courses, tricks, commands, games & exercises. ★ Watch step-by-step video instructions for every training exercise. ★ Use daily personalized training recommendations. ★ Set reminders for your pup's potty and training schedules. ★ Track & monitor your pup's training progress. ★ Strengthen your friendship. Bond with your best friend. ★ Easy to use Dog Clicker & Puppy Whistle. ★ Dog health reminders - Dogo informs you about your dog's health and upcoming vaccinations and grooming appointments. All in one place with the dog medication reminder! ABOUT Dogo App Dogo App is a training app for dog parents. It includes all the necessary commands like a dog clicker, different sounds, and the possibility to create an individual schedule for your pet. We have multiple training programs to choose from (Puppy Program, Basic Obedience, Impulse Control, Little Helper, Pleasant Walks, Potty Training, Puppy Bites, Stay Active, Strengthen Your Friendship, and more). In addition, dog parents can access +100 exclusive guided videos for all skills and behaviors (leash training, sitting, come, down, stay, puppy potty training, welcoming a newly adopted pet, puppy games, house training, stopping puppy biting, calm around other dogs, staying on a place, high-five, etc.), learn tricks, play games and enjoy the dog life with your pup. All you need to socialize, train, and bond with your dog is now on one app. TALK TO US We will do our best to make your Dogo experience as pleasant as possible. If you need any help, don't hesitate to get in touch with our customer service at support@dogo.app. DOGO SUBSCRIPTION You can try Dogo for 7 days with a free trial. After the free trial period ends, you will need to subscribe to Dogo. You can subscribe to Dogo by choosing from the following plans: – 1 month – 12 months The subscription automatically renews unless auto-renewal is turned off at least 24 hours before the end of the current period. You can also find us on: ★ Web: https://dogo.app/ ★ Facebook: facebook.com/dogoTrain/ ★ Instagram: instagram.com/dogoapp ★ TikTok: tiktok.com/@dogoapp Terms & Privacy https://dogo.app/terms-of-service/ https://dogo.app/privacy/

comments: ["At the start I set it up for a new pup, general obedience, potty training & got signed up for impulse control? How does that make sense. You're introducing a clicker immediately which I find an advanced training method & can very easily be done incorrectly especially because it was not properly explained how it's done. Price is off the charts. In person courses are cheaper. ONLY 7D FREE! Not saying it's a bad app but it's overloaded and inconvenient for first timers or quick exercises & ..money", "The interface is friendly but the dowside is that you cannot try any of the exercises without the 7 days trial or paying for it. I understand that financial support is needed, but people would be more likely to pay for the app if they had a few exercises to try. Even if there is that 7 days trial I don't want to put my card information until I'm sure I want to pay fully for it 😁", 'It looks promising but the fact that you can\'t start any of the classes without signing up for the trial is ridiculous Edit for the developer: I don\'t care that you CAN pay for the app. I would just like to see what I\'m signing up for beforehand. If you can\'t get to your "free" version without going THROUGH your paid version then what the hell is the point? Just make it paid and call it a day.', "This app is fantastic. Easily worth the money. My old girl is picking up new tricks and behaviours with ease! It's stimulating for her and she loves our sessions. Highly recommend! It teaches us humans how to teach our pups with step by step instructions, videos and feedback!", "OMG, what is the point of pretending this is anything but a subscription app, any and everything is locked out unless you subscribe. And even when you click continue for free, it's to subscribe to the trial, of your confidence is this small for free users, why would anyone actually use the paid for version? Just switch to a $40 purchase model. There's nothing to try if you're seeing what the app is like before purchase.", 'New puppy. I love the instructions which are clear concise and very helpful so far. This is day one. I will revisit this rating in order to provide a more thorough rating. Day 4 and I am finding Dogo to be absolutely fantastic. Day 29- my puppy and I are making tremendous strides in training. Again the feedback from the trainers is incredibly helpful. My friend and I are getting so much closer as a team.', "It's my favorite dog training app my puppy instantly learned how to sit It's very good to train your dog it's easy I really love this overall,I rate this a 5 star rating, it's the best app in the world. and also add some features to it, I'll really appreciate it notice this, there's no ads but can you make everything cheaper I can't get a new dog.", "I have my 5 month old collie and 8 year old Jack Russell training at the same time at different levels of obedience. Video tutorials are easy to follow and straightforward. I have subscribed to access the full content, which is fair enough. It is good training advice, and I can understand needing to pay for it. At £5.99 a month, you can use it 24/7, and another member of your household can download it and access the account. It's still cheaper than hiring a professional trainer.", "Confusing and too many pop ads for premium. I'm fostering a 15 month old Anatolian Shepherd and he's quite head strong. He was partially trained but there are things we need to work on. Anytime I go to start a lesson an ad pops up and I get sent back to the first page. I can't open the lesson. Very frustrating.", "App works great. Unfortunately the new update on June 21st has changed the UI for the calendar section to track things like wees and poos and it's terrible compared to the old design. It's so much harder to read at a glance and the whole days schedule no longer fits on one screen. Please go back to the old design without the stupid poo emojis or I am probs gonna can em my sub.", "I've never trained a dog and this app really truly does assist me. Amongst the basics, my pup can learn some fun tricks as well! I was skeptical at first especially that you have to pay for service, but I don't mind it all! You'd spend way more paying for obedience school", 'Directions are clear. You can\'t skip exercises that are already mastered. While the exercises aren\'t required to be done in a certain order, the next level are locked until the base is "completed". Different programs feature the same modules, but the modules aren\'t connected so the same exercise must be "taught" twice or more. Circles back to locked variations. Reminders are "on/off" not "set time" so it goes off at 10pm when I\'m in bed.', 'I cannot rate this app high enough, 5++ stars. Everything you need to train your dog at any age. The exercises have worked so well and my dog is learning quickly, much credit goes to the trainers who wrote the training manual and the feedback they give. This app has worked so well to teach me how to train my dog, the features really help me to tain my dog consistently throughout the day. Me and my pet are learning together with Dogo. Cannot recommend enough, get this app!', 'Can\'t change time to am/pm format in calendar. I hope this reaches the developers: most of us do not like to use 24 hour time format in the United States. So the calendar is annoying where we can\'t change that: makes me so some mental calculations every time I use it. Please add in the ability to change to am/pm (12 hr) format. Also: why is there an option for "wake up" but not for "went to sleep" or "bedtime"?', "This is a good app, especially as a first time dog owner. There are some improvements that could be made. The rating system for a lesson should match the lesson rather then just being generic because it doesn't always work e.g. on the puppy biting course, would be great if it was specific to puppy biting so I really know what behaviour I am looking for.", 'Works out well. I just did not understand how this program works so I went in and started the first exercise. Was a bit of a mess so I did it a few times over 2 days and than went in and looked at the next exercise. Which told me to do the first for longer now. Well I was way over that already. Now I know to just go in and do the next exercise without going on on my own. Sit and stay was no problem. One more thing...I am training the dog alone so I have no one to film me doing the exercise 🙃', "So far so good. I wish they had a button for the calendar when he doesn't pee when I take him out so that the reminder resets. It doesn't reset unless you put if he peed in place or had an accident.", "This app is not free like it says. Yes, they offer a 7 day free trial, but you have to put in all your banking information, and then yeah, you can cancel it after 7 days, but they still. Have your banking information!!! It also takes more than 7 days to know if the training that you're getting from the app is actually working for your dog.", 'Great information! Our first dog is trained very well, very focused and motivated. He\'s an agility "athlete"! Now we\'re using this same guidance to train our second corgi! Highly recommend starting your relationship with your dog with these guidelines! Almost gave 4* because the app layout can seem a bit convoluted.', "It was supposed to be free, but you need to buy a subscription to do ANYTHING in this app. Overall, I thing it would be a good app if you'd just mention that you need to buy the subscription with 7 days free trial.", "The app is really good, I love the family feature but I wish we could post pictures when it comes to the updates and appointments, for example when you put something about a vet visit you could take a picture of the dog at the vets office, or if it's a note for training to take a picture how well it's going, so all the family can see the growth progress as well as reading it", "Pretty great app so far, but I wish there was an option to skip certain lessons or skills. For example I don't see the need for the skill Touch and I want to skip it but I can't.", "I like the app and that it is set up with daily exercises . However I am doing the impulse control class and the exercises are random. I am on day 4 and it is having us do a down w30 sec stay ( down 3), but it hasn't even taught down yet. It's not teaching the basics and building, it's is generating 3 random exercises from the set of 17. I would like to keep the model of dailey exercises and games and have it build from intro to expert.", 'Love it so far, very straight forward set up, everything is easy to find and I love the informative videos demonstrating each task. Love it!', "If I install one more app, that isnt free. Is it so hard to quickly state in the ad that it's a monthly fee to use the app? Now, I'm not clicking on any more apps. They all cost. And the ones that's free are probably so crusty. Lol!", 'So far brilliant app. Explains a lot of reasons why we should do each little task. It has a purpose behind it. My puppy is 9 weeks old and has mastered sit already with this. I think he enjoys the attention he gets too with it. Definitely worth it.', "This app is actually helping me to train my dog. She's a stubborn bulldog/pit. After using doggo, I've noticed that she walks with a loose leash more frequently, and I can actually get her to sit patiently while I pour her food. Consistency is key. If you don't use the app, you'll be wasting your money. However, I'm genuinely surprised by how fast I got these results.", "It's mostly really good and I appreciate the simple straight forward directions and bite size chunks. - As mentioned by others the clicker is a good idea but in practice is hard to use while also holding treats and a lead. I bought a physical clicker almost straight away. - It's really hard to record training that you didn't use the app for. Eg. If I do some sit and stay training without starting the timer I can't then go back and record that without just like running out the timer afterward.", 'I like this app. It has forced me to see training in a different way and has worked wonders for our 7 month old husky. My only complaint is they need tutorials for what to do if your dog does poorly at a specific exercise. Instead you select how well they did and even if they did poorly they say "job well done" and move on. You can message them but it takes a while to hear back. Add a "how to adjust if they aren\'t understanding" feature and it would easily be 5 stars.', "I was giving up hope but this app makes things seem so simple, and where we've hit a hurdle the additional advice is spot on. I love the real trainer feedback.", "Only used it once or twice so far so good. I do like that the clicker is on the phone sonic I can't find mine or don't have it on me I can be consistent.", "This is not a free app. Once all set up I can't add the first potty time without a road block of starting a free trial or paying", "Fantastic app, highly recommended I am so glad I found this app, me and my family are training our puppy and it's great we can do it together on the same app, and even have the older dog on there to learn new stuff and be included. A year's subscription is great value and the dog trainers are really quick to respond to your videos and questions. Thanks team Dogo!", 'Would be a great app if able to pay for subscription. All training and lesson plans and command instructions are locked behind a pay wall. There is however a clicker and whistle available for use!', 'This is a great way to stay on top of progression and give good simple feedback. Wish there was a bit more repetition in the programs, where is the dog doesnt get 4 or 5 stars the exercise should repeat instead of continuing to progress. That being said the feedback and general build is great, awesome price too', "Ive only explored / used the app a couple times, but I like it. I just hate that so much content requires subscription and the cost is a bit high imo. I get app and content makers need revenue and I would consider $20/yr, but I'm not gonna pay $40/year to obtain guidance and info that can be found elsewhere online for free w/ a simple search. Perhaps I'm too cheap, but they should offer tiers of service for ppl who want access to all prewritten material w/o any personalized attention.", 'Very good app. Working my way through with my one year old and having a lot if fun. Looking through the exercises though I think a lot are at a novice level so before the subscription is up you would have completed them all. Having intermediary and advanced levels available would increase customer retention.', "It's unbearably detailed I wish I can have a feline version. This will help me in the long run of allowing both feline and canine to get along. When I'm done and alone.", "Well so far I am loving the Doggo app. I'm just using the basic one and not the premium. The basic one seems to have everything I need to help me train my dog. You pick the exercise or activity you want to do with your dog and it shows you step-by-step on how to do it with examples from other pet parents in short videos. It has a 2 minute countdown timer to do each training and also has a clicker and a whistle in the app. It makes training easier and fun for all.", 'A Stellar Dogo App Experience - Highly Recommended! The user-friendly interface and intuitive design make navigating the app a breeze. From the moment I downloaded it, I was pleasantly surprised by the seamless experience it provides. The app is organized in a logical and easy-to-follow manner, ensuring that I can quickly access the information I need.']

comments: ["This app is a very good up but there are few things I think it could be more better with, for example ; there should be an option to communicate as a free members cuz is not everyone that can afford to pay and the prices too are too high for subscription cuz there's no guarantee for you to get a perfect match by the end of month as a premium member. We should be able to search for a precise members. For example (verified profile only and search in more than 1 location at a time. etc..", "Of all the dating sites I've used, I've NEVER in my life seen so many scammers and catfish. I use the site via my mobile browser, but it's all the same. I've received messages from three different women with the SAME PICTURES, just different ages and names, and if they aren't catfishing, they need X # of dollars for (______). I get it. All African women aren't like that, but dang, this site takes the cake. My experience has not been that good. Y'all need to find better ways to vet women.", "U mean I can't read messages from my friends bse I haven't pay ,wat if I don't have money.u want me to download any app please help us because am going to delete your app it's not helping me at all many friends are sending me messages but I can't reply to them help me dats ma problem so me and chatting with my new friends I can't even send any message to ma friends I don't have money to for gold and premium so help me so dat I can chat with ma friends I will pay later when I have got money ok ..", "You don't even get a single free message or even see the messages people send to you unless you upgrade. Some free options will make the app better", "very simple to use, just that you need to have a premium membership to talk...and also it doesn't have to be that costly either", "You can't use the App well without you paying, even sending a message to a free or paid user it refuses. The funny thing is you'll receive a message and you can't even read without paying. If you are a free user find another App.", "Was chatting with a premium member and all of a sudden I can no longer chat with him why, he subscribed so how come I can no longer send a message across to him but he can, I'm disappointed", "Only scammers on this app. You're better off on Bumble, Hinge, etc. The choices may suck on those apps, but at least the people are real there. Afro Introdctuons is horrible.", "It's cool and I like the app but I think it would be better if newbies can be able to send messages for free for a short period of time before paying for their packages.", 'You have to pay for subscription before you can chat with someone and the subscription plan is too expensive. With some of the reviews I have read below, this app look like a scam app with a lot of fake profile', 'Free to sign up but you can read msg unless you pay for a premium acct starting at $20 a week is insane. With a high probability most of the profiles are fake or scammers, this app is super trash.', "Worst dating app ever!! Why isn't there even a trial period??? You can't chat before you subscribe and the subscription fee is highly extortionate...🤨🤨🙄😒 don't waste your data.", "19.99 a week for a membership is extortionate, an before they reply saying there's cheaper options, the other option is 16.99, still extortionate.. it doesn't even offer a free trial to see if it's worth paying for.. and unless you pay, the app is unusable, they keep telling people they offer free and paid memberships, making an account is the only thing thats free, then, even if you pay, the other person has to be a paying member also, otherwise you still can't chat, ridiculous", 'I had just created my account and while I was finishing up my profile, the app crashed. I tried to log back in and they said that my account was permanently terminated. I logged in a complaint with their customer support team and they wanted me to send a copy of my ID or passport. Not falling into that trap!!', "I like the app but then the real issue is you can't do quite a lot without having to pay so much. Imagine you have to pay as much as 9,000 naira monthly just to read your messages. That's too much. After this review up👆, I discovered that the one or two messages I could read before the review has been set such that I MUST make payments of 9,000 naira before I can read them. Afrointroduction are you mad at me for the sincere review I made?🤭", 'This app is not easy why did you suspended my profile without reason and when l send you a message on the email you tell me you hv reactivated it and when l open it tells me the same thing reactivate will take 48hours and these hours already passed so how should l trust you.', "I don't understand why you keep on telling me wrong email and it's my first time joining. If they said wrong password I would hv thought maybe I forgot. Kindly tell me which kind of email do you need? Am uninstalling it since I can't acces it", "it's good... The Perfect and best dating app I have ever used,, hopefully to meet my dream white man... plenty of cute single me and women there,I recommend everyone seriously seeking a friend, partner etc to join there", "the money needed is too much, money needed for upgrading is too much this app is not helping totally rubbish I will delete it, cause i can't reply messages cause I don't have such money for upgrading", 'I didn\'t like this app because am just new in a few days it started saying that "your account has been suspended" but I don\'t know the reason, I tried to reactivate,to upload my profile but it still saying the same', "messages can't be read or sent without paying unlike other apps which is a big difficulty here.No their isn't any free membership here you have to pay for everything", "I love this app because it gives a lot of information about it members but the subscription is very expensive and you can't even chat anyone, you should get free 3 days vip to know how it works", "the problem of this app is that you can not pay through mpesa they only need money express so if you don't have an ATM VISA you can't get anyone here!", "Please ADMIN, remove this message restrictions for standard members rather configure the app to be collecting your running charges through data subscription. Reduce the cost of membership subscription. it's too high and its discouraging people from joining afrorintroductions. Thank you", "Everything about this app is money. there should be at least one week grace for new members before subscription. if you can't give that, I will remove the app", 'Among the "Cupid" series of dating apps now run by Dating Group it has in my opinion one of the highest number of fake or "inactive" profiles...its purely geared towards profitability and the staff is changing profile names or headers and other parts of the profile without notification or my consent and than expects me to pay for that kind of service? Nope thank you!!! Lots of other apps where you can exchange messages for free 😉, like Okcupid for example...owned by Match Group, same as Tinder', "my thinking is that it should not attract any charges at all. But if it would attract charges, it shouldn't be at earliest stage at all. Allow the lovers to meet each other and progress . When the now see each other and agree and gave each other consent, little charges may be introduced. Thanks.", 'I love the app but befour you send a message to people...you must pay for premium', "I don't really see anything wrong with a person supporting his spouse .you guys keep sending warning messages not to give anyone money", "still new. so not sure how it works. but why can't I read someone message, I have to subscribe first", 'The subscription is just too expensive, N9000 per month, just for sending and receiving messages, come on, this is very unrealistic, plus looks like there are more bots than actual human beings in the app. I think one should be able to send a couple limited messages, but you will now upgrade to premium of you want unlimited messages, still at a reasonable price.', 'At first I hated this app because everyone is too young to date and lives on another continent, but I have had some great conversations with some really cool people that I would not have met otherwise. I changed my profile to just meet new people. The app itself is just ok, you get notifications and then have to sort through numerous pages to find them because everything displays out-of-order. And often there are no notifications, you just happen across messages you missed way down the list.', 'Afrointroduction is now doing the most, I love enjoy catching up my matches, good works!.....', 'it is good app, but at least they should allow free messages for one day for the newest.', "Highly strict. By now, I've not been granted full access having paid for platinum member.", "This app is good though but they're always ignoring my email address and I don't know why, please you people should do something about it", "This is requesting for upgrading monthly payment. I can't read messages sent to me because the app is not a free app. Please make it to be free and easy to use. I have a lot of messages, but I can't open it. Please do something about this afro introduction... How can I pay 9 to 36 thousand monthly just for messages.", "Please the money is the issue is way too high just for chatting..as in what are you guys selling and what are we buying that such amount will be paid..frankly speaking that money is way too big..you can't even read a message sent to you by someone...atleast even if we have to pay let it be maybe after a while but not that amount. Thanks", 'Too many fake accounts, like chatting with bots or employees of the app.nothing serious ever comes out.get block for no reason after multiple good conversation.', "I can't get accesses to my chats it's saying I'm suppose to upgrade and it's not working even after trying to upgrade"]

title: CFish: Christian Dating App
description:
CFish is one of the best dating apps for christian singles to chat and mingle with other Christians. Here single Christians can easily look for a God-centered relationship with like-minded singles that share your beliefs.

Unlike other online Christian dating sites or apps, CFish has the most serious users you can communicate with because our support team will manually review every user profile and do our best to eliminate scammers. We hope to create one clean and serious dating community for the people in those Christian denominations such as Baptist, catholic, Charismatic, Protestantism, Orthodoxy etc.. You will have the highest chance to find your ideal match here.

How does CFish app work?

- Chance -
Browse profiles of local Christian singles based on your filter

- Boost -
It can boost up your profile in "Chance" page, so you will get more matches

- Square -
Share the love, faith and hope with brothers and sisters in Christian community

- Talks -
 Communicate with other Christians by our message system

Create your account for free to join our Christian community and meet new quality Christian singles today.
summary: Serious Dating App for Christian Singles to Meet, Date & Mingle with Friends
