comments: ['This app overall is fairly fluid and easy-to-follow when setting up a profile and searching for matches. However, unless I\'m missing something (I\'m still fairly new), the app frustratingly will not update the locations of the people in the "chances" section. I\'ve filtered my location repeatedly and I still find girls from all across the country and rarely in my home state. I also feel the subscription, though cheaper than other apps, is not worth the money. I\'ll update after some time.', 'The filter feature is useless. Filter by county is useless. It\'s either they don\'t have enough users or this feature is broken. I have to switch to filter "any" in order to find anyone.... Also, you have to paid before you can change filter selections. In my opinion, don\'t pay for this app. So many useless features you don\'t need.', "Be wary with this app, especially if paying. I did a one month buy and of the four woman who messaged me today, three went unavailable shortly after. That seems to mean that they were either bots (who have VIP status) and were deleted or CFish is setting up fake profiles to message you, enticing you to pay. Also, if you do pay, they don't have an option to turn off auto renewal. You basically have to do so via Play Store. That's really bad on their part.", 'This christian dating app is very good, easy to operate, especially smooth. The most important thing is that all the functions are in line with the requirements of christian friends. I used a lot of apps before, like bumble, hinge, pof, ect.. but they did not achieve the purpose I wanted at all. Here, I find the one in my mind.', 'Garbage app. Didn\'t even get to use it. I created my account, didn\'t receive any confirmation emails or anything and my account was suspended right after creation. The app never actually loaded. I went to update my settings/preferences, everytime I hit update I would get a dialogue that said "Sorry for the inconvenience. Your account has been suspended. We need to confirm the security of your account." Really disappointed and I\'ll be uninstalling the app. Didn\'t even get to use it.', "One month later the app is working better as a paid subscriber. At least I can log in and out now without having to create a new profile every time as the information including password are saved. There just isn't enough bandwidth to IM quickly so a lot of patience is still required. This is the biggest drawback of using this app. Profile verification could be improved. I have found/reported multiple profiles using similar pictures but different names. Please allow docs and pics to be sent too!", "I give this christian dating app a five-star rating and would like to recommend it to all christian singles. In fact, this dating app didn't start out perfect, and it probably had a lot of drawbacks. For example, in previous versions, it crashed quite a bit, didn't work out of range search, and didn't get as many users as christianmingle, cdff. However, their developers worked very hard and had a very good attitude. Every time I complained to them about the problem of the app, they would reply to me very quickly and solve it in a very short time. And they are willing to listen to users' opinions to improve the product, so now I think cfish is a very good dating app, with smooth experience and unique features, it is worth trying.", "I love this Christian dating app. In the past, I had been using some popular dating apps, such as bumble, hinge, pof, etc., but these dating apps had a lot of users, but it was still hard to find a single Christian.This dating app is a great opportunity for Christians to meetup and date each other, and the design and functionality are great, at least so far I've been comfortable with it.", 'So far so good, still scanning through it. There are certain feature as a user I would have like to use seeing my faith differences with the many. For some demoniations you have many choices from other none. You would have to click through every picturer to see who is who. Filters are limited', "They charge you communicate with other users. It seems almost every other use is free, basic searching preference, updating your profile, searching I your city. But they don't tell you about the $20 a month charge just for basic messaging. And don't get me started on the $40 a month plan they have! I feel like you're taking money that should be going into a church fund. Just ask people to donate, and have basic communication abilities for the free account users. You can charge 4 the other boost.", "This is a good christain dating app. It's better than christian mingle, crosspaths, pof dating apps in terms of design and functionality. There are a lot of features that are specifically designed for christians, for example, to post verses and anonymous confessions, and there's also a boost to your profile in the search page, which is very good and I hope you'll continue to improve it.", 'Too many fake profiles, same persons with a different angle or background. Noticed photos being used across other states of numerous lookalikes with different backgrounds. It was the same females, must be quadruplets, lol. Even got a random message from some "girl" telling me to text. C\'mon no one is falling for that.', "So far so good, love the free boost but can use more things such as add photos option, maybe video/audio option? Overall, I recommend using this christian app the response rate is better than other dating apps I've used in the past. Messaging needs to be fixed as well sometimes it doesn't get sent.", 'This app has almost no filters, no settings, nothing. Other apps you can put an age range of who can contact you and there are more details so it makes it easier with less wasting of your time. That being said it seemed to run well and was not laggy.', 'This dating app is very good. It provides dating services for Christian friends. Unlike tinder, bumble and hinge, you have to screen a lot of people who want to look for hookup. Here, the vast majority of users are looking for serious love, except for a few scammers, I hope you can add authentication function, so that it is easier to identify cheaters. God bless you, meet me here.', "If I could I would give this app zero stars. If you don't have enough staffing to answer tech calls during a pandemic then don't have an app. This company charged me after I had already tried ending my subscription. I tried calling them more than once to discuss it but there was no answer until I finally emailed them, and even then they could not help me be refunded. Waste of money and time. A lot of people on this app are just looking to hookup or are trying to scam you. Would not recommend!", 'I highly recommend this christian dating app because its really good and Ive found my match on it, its better than christian mingle or other dating apps. First of all, the function is very simple and easy to use. You just need to search for the Christian singles you are looking for through the filter. In addition, the function of anonymous confession is also very characteristic. One user replied to my confession, which moved me a lot. The only disadvantage is that there are a lot of scammers, you need to be careful to identify them, you can also report them, so they will be deleted quickly.', 'No way to communicate with other people without having to pay a ridiculous amount. And their reasoning behind their decision is to keep people from being bothered. Bothered by who? People can still bother others when they pay. There are better ways/steps to get to message people, without being bothered, other than having to charge people a ridiculous amount.', "I highly recommend this christian dating app because it's really good and I've found my match on it, it's better than christian mingle or other dating apps. First of all, the function is very simple and easy to use. You just need to search for the Christian singles you are looking for through the filter. In addition, the function of anonymous confession is also very characteristic. One user replied to my confession, which moved me a lot. The only disadvantage is that there are a lot of scammers, you need to be careful to identify them, you can also report them, so they will be deleted quickly.", 'Not a user friendly app and contains all religions. With all due respect, I thought this was a Christian dating app but one needs to first pay in order to specify preferred religion or faith. I also selected a profile to view and was not able to exit the profile unless I wrote a message to the person.', "It's not a free app when you get to make a account, search around through profiles and when you finnaly find one and form a message it tells you that you need to pay in order to send massages. After you've composed a message you thinks good and hit send then it pops up. If you're going to make people pay just say it at the start not when someone finds someone they are interested in.", "I've been using this christian dating app for a few months, and it was completely free at first, but recently it started charging, and I've seen a lot of other users complaining, and it's normal, people want free. At first, I also complained about the charge to their customer service staff, but the customer service staff responded to me politely, and I can understand that only charging can provide better service. And their customer service staff was very patient. I didn't understand how boost works, so I sent a letter to ask. Anyway, it's a great dating app, god bless.", 'I keep trying to sign up and after answering all of the questions about me, I upload a photo but then when I put in my Nickname and hit "Save", it keeps telling me in red at the top "username is less than 6 characters".... Wellllll there isn\'t anywhere that I can find that ever asks for a username, so I haven\'t even got a place to put a username so I can\'t even enter a username if I wanted to on this app. I can\'t seem to find a place where it asks for username anywhere at all in the setting up of a new account where when I clicked on "Join Us". When I click there and fill out everything, which I have done 3 times now, it just keeps saying the same thing in red ""username is less than 6 characters". I am clueless how to JOIN. HELP PLEASE!! I will gladly change this review if someone can help me solve my problem.', "Waste of time. Bad filter options, bad layout, doesn't let you choose your correct denomination. The list goes on...just don't waste your time. This app needs major updates.", "Cfish app is so easy to use, both in design and function, that it's clearly better than other christian dating apps. Because I've used most of these dating apps. The design of christian mingle and cdff is outdated, and fth is too simple and lacks Christian elements. Instead, much of Cfish's functionality is geared towards Christian members, such as verse, anonymous confession, etc., a pretty good dating app for christians.", "I thought this was a good free app but this is just another money grabbing scheme. I found a few matches who I wanted to get to know and when I message them, the messages to the ladies didn't get dilivered and showed a red exclaimation mark next to the message which means message didn't get dilivered. When I clicked on the message then the membership icon poped up which was also ridiculously high just to chat with someone. hence, uninstalled these greedy developers app.", 'Im a single christian, and Ive tried dating apps like tinder, bumble, and hinge, all of which have a large user base, but its hard for these mature singles to find serious christian dates. Like tinder, too many young guys and girls in there. Until my friend recommended me to try some christian dating apps, I tried some related apps, and I thought cfish was actually a better one. The pleasant design and interesting functions helped me find many like-minded friends, which was much better than christian mingle, cdff, whose design style was too outdated.', "Cfish is a dating app that claims to be a serious platform for Christian singles to meet, date, and mingle with friends. However, there are a few issues to consider. First, there are other religions available to select as your own, including Muslims and Jews, which are not Christian. Additionally, while it's possible to filter by religion, it's only available with a premium account. Furthermore, you cannot message a single person on this app without having a premium account.", "This christian dating app is perfect for catholics. I've been using this meetup app for a few months and I've found a lot of catholic singles in it. They're very friendly and we often talk about religion. Although I haven't found my true love on this christian bumble app yet, I think it will happen sooner or later, because this app is really easy to use, fully functional, and can also post anonymous confessions, which is very suitable for us catholic.", "I've fairly new to Cfish, and I have already had an incredible experience. The app is really simple and easy to use, and a lot of the people I've talked to have been really good people. Obviously, online dating is what you make it to be. So if you want good results, just be patient, use your judgment, and come ready to have a good conversation. All in all, it's a great dating site, better than pof or meet me, because it's just for christian singles, haha.", "Cfish is definitely a very cool Christian dating site with a lovely design and unique features for us christians, haha. I've used dating sites like Christian mingle, hinge, pof and so on before, but they're either staid in design or have a hard time finding friends who have faith. Cfish, on the other hand, is a website specifically designed for Christian singles that does the same thing, like you can post verses, which is pretty good, worth a download and five stars.", 'Would be a good idea for preference about the distance and allow messaging without purchasing. I rather at least be able to exchange a few words with someone before having to make a purchase!', "This is crazy! I paid the subscription on the first day and i sent a lot of texts to see if I would have any response, to see if it was real that there were fake profiles here and the weird part is I got just one response and was only one text. after I asked on a post if there were any real people there,my post got under review and my account eliminated! The same day. Im demanding my money back..... They don't deserve even half of a star, this is FRAUD.", "All 5 and 4 star reviews are fake This app is designed to take your membership fee money. There is no service, the profiles inside are fake too. I have gotten zero responses and have sent out over 20 messages. The entire thing is fake! Also paid the fake membership fee and the account doesn't have payment options, it takes your money and leaves you with nothing to verify or way to see transaction history.", "I'm fairly new to this dating app. The app itself is great. Just the messaging doesn't work well at all. I'll get a message from someone and I reply back to them. Either they are not getting my messages or they are ghosting me. I'm a paying member right now. If this continues I'll quit my subscription.", "Cfish is definitely a very cool Christian dating site with a lovely design and unique features for us christians, haha. I've used dating sites like Christian mingle, hinge, pof and so on before, but they're either staid in design or have a hard time finding friends who have faith. Cfish, on the other hand, is a website specifically designed for Christian singles that does the same thing, like you can post verses, which is pretty good, worth a download and five stars.", 'Hi everyone, the app could be good. But sadly scammers take advantage of these apps. I had a bad experience with a scammer. So please be careful. I am not saying the app is or that everybody in the app is a scam but that you have to be careful. I would love for the developer of this app to contact me so I can share the details.', "Very quite and not much around locally. Good thing it's free ish and just seeing how it goes. Good app though. As for scammers not many and it does get dealt with. Hopefully someone local will appear. Customer service very good.", "App keeps crashing every time I open it. I've sent a crash report. Is there an update coming to fix this for certain devices. Thanks.", "Have to upgrade to send or receive messages. No other way as this app doesn't even have a profile swipe matching. No local contacts anyway. Definitely avoid"]

title: Match and Meet - Dating app
description:
Match & Meet is a unique dating application where you can chat with like-minded people in a special chat that instantly translates messages into your native language.

Take a short psychological test and find out your best match. Find attractive people close to you who share the same interests, and get to know them before meeting in real life. Our free dating app will help you communicate without boundaries and find the right match online. Join thousands of single people looking for a real relationship. 

3 Reasons to download the Match & Meet app:

1. Meet interesting users nearby
2. Explore people according to interests before dating online
3. Find the right match for yourself

What else can you do with Match & Meet?

1. View photos, browse through photo albums
2. Like and comment on the best photos
3. Add the most interesting profiles to your favorites
4. Translate messages into your native language and understand all chats
5. Reply to all messages in a polite and friendly way

Looking to make new friends in your city?

Find new friends in your city to chat online, meet in person, and have a great time! Match & Meet  is available in the most cosmopolitan cities around the world, with a large community of singles looking for a date or relationship.

How to use the Match & Meet app?

- Just download the Match & Meet app on your mobile phone or tablet
- Start chatting in real-time right now

Welcome to Match & Meet! A fascinating world of real live communication!

Discover a new form of online dating without any language barriers. Match & Meet will help you find the best matches according to your location, interests, and preferences. Start meaningful relationships with nearby people and chat before meeting. 

Match & Meet is an innovative dating app that allows you to meet new people without any limits! Explore your matches anywhere in the world, and communicate in any language.

Online dating made simple.

Connect with relevant users who share the same interests as you, understand them in any language, and enjoy chat with your matches. Match & Meet provides a unique way to get to know fellow singles. Start chatting with people who share the same interests and locations as you!

User protection

We strictly prohibit all forms of profanity, nudity, and obscenity. Match & Meet users can report bad behavior at any time by contacting us at support@corp.loka.world.

Match & Meet is free to download. If you want to get the most from the app, you can subscribe to our optional subscription product They Stream Premium (monthly - $14.99,  3-monthly - $29.99, 6-monthly - $49.99, 12-monthly - $69.99). The prices may vary per country and are subject to change without notice.

* if you choose to use our free trial, any unused portion of the free trial period will be forfeited when you purchase a subscription to that publication

Your personal data is stored securely in Match & Meet - be sure to read our privacy policy and terms:

title: Black White Interracial Dating
description:
Interracial Dating and match: The New Enlightenment

Less than a century ago, interracial dating was something you didn’t talk about, and something to hide if you did prefer a person of a different color.  There were few places you could go to safely without causing some sort of scandal, and even fewer people who were willing to listen with understanding.  

Maybe it was the rhythm and blues saturating the basements of late night entertainment.  Maybe it was a society lifting out of the Great Depression, with more tolerance accompanying their more affluent life styles.  Maybe it was the boldness of writers, spokes people and celebrities campaigning for civil rights, but by the 1960’s, interracial dating slowly became more acceptable.  

The changing times brought its own set of problems.  Even as the work force became more integrated, with minorities and women stepping into roles once designed for white, professional males, and public places ceased separating or refusing services to minorities, interracial dating was still awkward.  It was an era of general agreement on civil rights, but there weren’t very many among the Depression Years parents who were prepared to bring racial integration into the home. 
 
The Millennial Perspective

The awkward early years of racial integration jump-started interracial dating.  Today, seven percent of the population claims a mixed race heritage.  The number is growing rapidly, with most interviewee’s stating pride in their multiracial origins and claiming their heritage has made them more open to other cultures. 
 
Seven percent is significantly higher than in the 1970’s, when only one percent declared a mixed race background, but analysts feel these number are actually only about half the actual percentage, as many who are mixed race claim only one ethnic background.  The majority of those who claim only one race are middle-aged or older.  
From Age to Regional Location

The younger you are, the easier it is to find a partner for interracial dating.  The twenty to thirty year old set are generally very casual and already have a wide mixture of multi-cultural and multi-racial friends.  Tolerance, however, especially by family and community, can vary greatly according to demographics.  In many areas, especially regions that historically disapproved of mixed race dating, there may no longer be taboos, but the cultural clash still exists.  The family, and even your date, might have stereotypical views of your personal tastes and behaviors.  

Crossing the barriers where racial misconceptions still exist takes fortitude and patience.  Interracial views are changing rapidly but not racial views.  You may experience those uncomfortable moments of somebody going out of their way not to offend you, anxieties concerning appropriate behaviors, or even suspicion and reserved behaviors.  

Unless you are dating someone with exactly the same historical background, social status and religion, you are still going to be challenged by your date’s customs.  For many races, the customs are more engrained than color, status or ancestral origins.  Religion may be an important influence on their lives, even if they no longer declare a religious preference, as they will make time for the traditional values of their family. 
 
But that’s part of what interracial dating is all about.  It’s an opportunity to take a broader look at the world around us, to improve our communications with others, and learn about differing cultures and customs that can enrich our everyday lives.

comments: ["The app is good in its variations of the people using it. However, I wish they warn you that your messages are no longer readable/accessible to those to whom you sent them if you're not a premium member after a while. Also, there's a lot of people claiming to be from where they're not. Is there no way that you can force people to at least be honest about their physical location, like ensuring that if I was somewhere in Africa or Asia, only countries in those continents are shown in the options?", "So many scammers and phishers. My inbox is FULL of blocked profiles that I've forwarded to customer service, but it doesn't stop! Ex. 'Adam' has multiple profiles with different variations of the name, same goofy arse photo and FOREVER sending the exact same exhausted message requesting me to call them. I've forwarded this info multiple times, yet it doesn't stop. There was a profile with Justin Timberlake's as the main photo! I HAD TO VERIFYMY PHOTO AND ACCOUNT WITH MY DRIVER'S! WTH?! TRASH!", "App is only a gateway for scammers. Tiny, TINY percentage of genuine users. As a guy, after a week of use, 100% of my contacts have been 30-year-old (+/- 3 yrs) women from Ghana. They are nearly all premium members and will always ask to communicate off the site, usually through WhatsApp. They have a photo verification system with instructions to provide an image of a government-issued ID with instructions to NOT block out personal information. They're stealing user images and personal info.", "Feedback take long and I wish there was an option of contacting a person privately. U pick interest and it just stops there. Let's get to real relationships otherwise the app is good.", "Another cash grab dating app. Don't waste your time. You will get bombarded with messages from various countries in Africa. Obviously, fake scammers. Even when you block them, they can still message you. On top of all this, they don't let you send a message to someone until you pay. Even POF lets you send 1 message every 24 hours free.", 'You have to pay just for the simple privilege of being able to message the matches you even get. Meaning in essence that there is no real free to flay way of using this app. Everything about this app is designed around pigeon holing people, ideally desperate men into no other avenue but paying to have the restrictions the app lifted so they can maybe have success on it. This is late stage capitalism at its finest ladies and gents', "I'm uncertain about this app. The purpose for me joining was to meet non-black men. Yet, I've mainly seen black men on there. So far I've received messages from black men. Which is a demographic I'm not interested in.", "Can't message without paying. Pointless. 99% of profiles are fake. This app is so bad it's actually kinda hilarious.", 'App has no defects but by authorizing debit,credit,visa and mastercards cards you totally complicate the subscribing experience.No Mpesa billing you are very unfair.it means the relationships are categorized for only Banks plastic monetary transactions.i am sure many are willing and have money but,even you must be consinderate.moreover you have very high billing charges .', 'Perfect 👌spot to find your soulmate. However, scammers👽 are also there, just be careful🥷', "As far as I can tell it's a quality app! Easy access and use. A good amount of users to increase likely hood of matches. And various features to help you out. Finally the app ensures your privacy and security well. I'd recommend it! To anyone. Looking for an interracial hookup. Ya'know. Definitely cool though because compared to apps like Tinder, or Bumble, or Hot or Not, you know that people want to hook up. There's no awkwardness. But in those other ones, you always have to read those profiles", "Majority of the women are indeed beautiful, but there from countries I've never seen before or heard of. Great conversation but leading to nowhere. When you save your settings in the filter settings, it changes by itself after you switch pages. I believe it's a default setting that resets each once one leaves. But overall, great way to meet a potential significant other.", "Bunch of scammers and bots messaging from Africa even though I have distance limits enabled. Don't waste your time", "CONs: Since launch in '18, the cost has doubled. NO free initiating messages, even if matched -- meaning, this is NOT free for at least one of the two parties in a match (you can respond if messaged). A 1-yr subscription (2x 6-month sub) is $140 - comparable to Lifetime Bumble sub.🌹feature is microtransaction money grab. PROs: seems to have large-ish user base, (heavy on green card seekers), private photo folder. SUMMARY: cannot recommend, too expensive, no 2-way free messaging matches.", "Worst dating app ever!! My profile has been suspended for several weeks, no contact, no explanation, nothing! I have tried to contact the site on several occasions but the form has a non-robot number at the end and this is completely unreadable, don't waste your time!!! Rubbish. Well week 15 and still no contact from the site. Don't waste your time. oh and the contact email doesn't work either!! GIVE YOU MY USERNAME, HOW? NEITHER YOUR CONTACT FORM OR SUPPORT EMAIL WORK PROPERLY ?", "This is a organized plenty of fish. Very similar, very poor matching abilities. Doesn't allow you to even really get a good understanding or view of the other person. Lots of men on here lying about age etc(non verified profiles), no filters (you must pay). Very poor layout and the notifications are never accurate. This is probably not going to change the app or cause for any transformation of it but this app has terrible algorithm and any additional feature that is pretty much basic costs you.", "The app has issues, but they don't really interfere with the user experience all that much. And surprisingly the paid version has been a more positive experience than the competition (Tinder, Bumble). I see why it has the high rating that it does. Admittedly, it feels pretty weird to sign up for a racially-themed dating service (I can't tell if it makes me a racist or the opposite), but the result so far seems to be about as close to normal dating as one could hope for in these nutty times.", 'This app is creative and really allows for you to give a well detailed description of what you are looking for. There are so many different ways to show you are interested in someone too! From likes, to messages, and favorites, it is so vast! And on top of that, the help center is so great! I sent something in and within an hour I had a response and solution! That is something I have seen no where else. Overall love the app and will for sure continue using!', "This app has some great potential. I got two connections in my town within the first 5 minutes of using it. It's quick and straight to the point. The only downside is that you have to pay in order to initiate message people though it's free to reply messages. I like the features it has though. The app is looking fantastic as of right now though. Even though you have to pay to message I still give the app 5/5. There are lots of hotties and lots of nice pictures.", 'Really easy to use and lots of people to meet', 'Great App when looking for singles. I used it a couple of time and I got meet some great people . The app is amazingly user friendly and easy to use. I was able to match to singles based on my preferred ethnicity. height, location and age. Love the updates which are pretty great and make the experience very wonderful. Great job guys, much appreciated.', 'Very exceptional and great app please continue to improve 💖', "Too many Ghanaian scammers, bots, fakes on there, lucky I haven't paid for anything. Sort this out or you will lose all the genuine users", "It's actually a good dating app even for the free version, the only thing that needs attention is the number of fake scammer profiles. I get a lot of likes but still gotta move on to the next person. I have met some nice real people on here, though just haven't found the one I'm looking for. This app needs a better system that stops the creation of fake profiles and blocking them.", "Still garbage. All the messages you receive are from people from the other side of the world. You can't message here to see if there's real profiles. Waste of time and a horrible app on top of it. It's always losing connection", "This app asks for my location but then it allows me to get messages from people all over the world. I keep getting men messaging me from England, Australia, and Africa. I am in the U.S. I gave the app two stars but came back and changed it to one because there are some nice looking men on there but I don't want to date a man that's not in my same state let alone same country. Plus the age preferences don't work either this app is the worse. Do NOT download this app a waste of space and time!!!", "It's a decent app. The only thing I really don't like is if you are not upgraded, your match isn't upgraded, then you can't talk to them. Most dating apps should allow that or even limit to how much talking you could do cause if you can't talk to them after matching, then what's the point? That's just wrong. Not everyone can afford to upgrade to membership. I'm fine not seeing other things but messaging should be free or limited. I matched and can't talk to them at all.", 'When I passed my application and was leaded to the app, I just felt so much better and couldnt wait swiping around. Ive been using BlackWhiteDating for a couple of weeks, and I found it to work quite well. All the key features of modern dating app are here: swiping gestures to let you easily like and pass people, sending instant messages to contact matches. BlackWhiteDating also has some quality features that just make it nicer and simpler to find people near around. The online customer service is also a nice touch. It helps me a lot to figure out this app. It has to have 6 stars not just five, one more should be given to their great customer service.', 'Easy to use and navigate. Reasonable membership rates. Only thing is not enough matches in my area. Only 4 stars because it can take up to 2 days for pic approval. Also it would be nice to check off & delete messages without having to read them first. I noticed a few crude/ offensive pics that were approved. Def. PLENTY of other Apps for that...', "No matter what you have on your setting you get people from Africa sending messages. What's even more annoying is getting spam from people sending their photo and WhatsApp. Try to click on the profile and the user is no longer available. Not worth your time for the free version definitely don't pay for it.", "Crappy swipe app. Can't filter well. They want to charge way too much for very little service. Very few local people, most are just looking for hook ups. Most of the guys are from out of country. Questionnaire questions are disgusting and not conducive to forming a relationship", "They have a real big problem with African scammers. There is no way of filtering out messages to just include your country, at least not for free. Makes me believe either they don't care or they just want you to pay money to make it go away. I get several messages a day, all obvious scammers. This app is a serious dumpster fire.", "thank you for this service. in this crazy world we live in, I work a lot and don't actually have as much time as I would like but this gets right to the point so thank you!", "Don't bother. Pretty much all the messages you're going to get are scams trying to get you to use WhatsApp. I know WhatsApp is used to phish your information, so DON'T USE IT! Also, the verification process is extremely worrying as they want you to use a driver's license or other photo ID with damaging information on it to verify.", "As a guy who is always busy with work and hardly any time for a decent social life, am glad to have come across this white girl app. I like that it has a very interactive interface, nice features to keep you engaged. I've been using this app for a while now and I've met some really interesting people. I especially like the location search feature which enables you to chat with anyone in the world. Also the ability to use your location to find people around you. The app generally has a classy fee", "Ugh. Dozens of invites from Africa from types outside what I put on my profile, which specifies my state ONLY. Notifications don't work. I have notifications turned on but do not get any. I'm assuming the messages I sent to my interests are not getting notifications, either. So, if they've stopped checking the app because of all the misfires, they won't get a message from me, a potentially viable match IN THEIR STATE, COUNTY, OR CITY IN THE USA. This is not user error. It's a trash fire.", "You never get any notifications unless you actually go in the app. Many people haven't been on for months and it might be because they forgot about it, possibly due to zero notifications. I believe this app works but it seems most make a profile and they're not seen online again. Please fix this issue. Also, it's be great to show the last time people were online so we'd know what's going on...", 'Love this amazing app. I have tried no fewer than a dozen dating apps, and finally i have found one that works like a charm. The app found me many single women in and around my city, all real people. I have, as a matter of fact, starting chatting and sharing photos with a few. Looks like this time i will find real loving after all, fingers crossed. I recommend this app to everyone.', "So many full fake people on here it's unbelievable fake pictures big scammers mostly from Africa and it really really is a good program but because you guys don't have a way of filtering the bad people out it becomes very bad... Plus it freezes up you have to wait like 3 minutes for it to actually start working again and once it starts working again it's okay but that beginning part when you first log into it freezes and freezes you got just get through that..", "This app exceeded my exceptions. I was really skeptical at first as I've tried many dating apps. But turns out this is the dating app I'm going to spend the most time on. It's different, just how I like. I love being able to connect with different personalities and especially people from different nationalities, cultures, colors, etc. Trust me, even tho you might be skeptical at first, I recommend you to try this app. It's great and you will guarantee meet new awesome people.."]

title: DogLog - Track your Pet's Life
description:
DogLog is an easy-to-use pet care app that makes pet ownership less stressful. It helps dog owners track their pet’s health, coordinates daily pet-related tasks, and lots more! DogLog is great for single pet parents and for families and has been downloaded by +100,000 pet owners.

PUPPY OWNERS
1) Track your puppy's training.
2) Understand your puppy's potty schedule to get them potty trained.
3) Set reminders for upcoming vaccination and record vaccination dates. 

OWNERS WITH SICK OR ELDERLY PETS
1) Track your pet's symptoms to understand if they are getting better.
2) Share activity and symptoms data with your vet.
3) Set reminders for giving medicine to your pet so you never miss a dose. 

PET SITTERS AND DOG WALKERS
1) Add your pet sitters and walkers to your Pack so all activities get recorded.
2) Pet sitters/walkers can add photos to your Pack so you never miss a moment.
3) Rest assured that your pet is taken care of.

Don't spend any more time wondering if your dog has been taken care of, download DogLog and enjoy the serenity of always knowing how your dog's day is going.

BENEFITS
1. Form a "pack" with your fellow dog caretakers
2. Log activities, such as giving food, going on a walk, and giving medication
3. Add comments to activities to provide extra information
4. Get notified when activities are logged for your pet with alerts. 
5. Create reminders and alerts so you never forget to take care of your pet. 
6. Use the Statistics page to get insights about your dog’s life
7. Share photos and messages to fellow caretakers with just a few taps.
8. Export data to share with your vet

ACTIVITIES YOU CAN LOG: 
- Food
- Water
- Treat
- Walk
- Pee
- Poop
- Sleep
- Teeth brushing
- Grooming
- Training 
- Medicine
- Custom - Anything else you want

Oldest version we support android 5.1
Icons Provided by Icons8

comments: ["Have been using doglog for a couple years now, it's one of the few apps that I use every single day. I'd be lost without it. There've been a few bugs along the way but they are always responsive and fixed quickly. I especially like some of the recent changes to the events like the drop-down in Medicine to specify the type. It's a lifesaver for multi-carer packs & dogs with health issues, being able to easily create a log of everything to share with the vet is priceless.", "Fantastic app for monitoring your pet's day-to-day life. We had a cat with several health issues and DogLog allowed us to track her health and daily routine easily and effectively. As a result, we were fully prepared for vet appointments with a concise record of her progress and, in turn, the vet could provide more effective medical care for her. Highly recommend this all for any pet owner.", "I like the app as it is very useful to be able to quickly make notes about your dog that will be organised and sorted in a nice way so you can easily go back to it. However a few things could be improved. One thing is the weight curve. The X-axis should be your pet's age, not the number increment of your measurement. If you don't weigh your pet continuously you will not see the slopes of weight gain/loss as realistic in the time dimension.", "The application doesn't allow me to put in the breed of my dog from my profile. Also, all info I inserted got deleted the moment I pressed 'back'button even though I had saved it. I'm deleting this app and finding a working one!", "Great and simple way to track daily activities, as well as medications. I added my dogs exact medication by name (custom) and a few other things specific to her. I decided to get premium so I can view the usual time or day we do certain things, and it has really helped me plan out schedules. It's super easy to use and pretty inexpensive for the information you get access to.", "It's pretty good. I've been using it for about 1 yr now. No ads everywhere and I like that I can filter by event categories. Only problem I have is that I can't delete entries when clicking the delete button. Edit button works but not delete", "This seems like a fairly helpful app and I love that you can share with a pack. I need to monitor blood sugar checks, urine checks, etc. You can make the categories but I really need a graph like the temp feature. I'm using a diabetic pet specific app but it is not stable. If this app grows to that level I would likely pay as the other features seem solid.", 'Any useful analytical data is locked behind a premium fee that does not justify its cost. I can do the same stuff with a free Google form and spreadsheet', 'Perfect for keeping track of toilet routines. Can adapt new icons for other things to track. Very useful', "does exactly what I need it to: helps clear up confusion about who took the dog for a walk and when to help us avoid messy accidents and be aware of our pooch's schedule. the ONE reason this isn't 5 stars for me is the lack of dark mode because this app blinds me every night i take my dog for s walk. otherwise, perfect little simple app.", "Love the simplicity of the interface with the option to add more activities (repeating for a common task or once, like a skunk attack!). Tracking my 11 week old puppy for the past 2 weeks has been extremely helpful. I can see patterns in what times he eats, when we go outside, when he's most likely to have an accident. would be better if you could adjust the time of the event as you are entering it instead of defaulting to current time. Slow app loading screen can be frustrating.", 'Very user friendly interface. Simple to use. The free version has enough features to get started with what appears to be paid for optional extras, which appear useful but not essential. So, you can get started for free and add the extras later, which is nice. Non-intrusive ads too. It has been very useful for us where there are six people plus two dogs in our pack, as we can each log our shared responsibilities and keep track of things. Very useful app.', 'Great app, especially for pups with multiple caregivers so you\'re not constantly texting each other "did you walk the dog before you left?". Intuitive and the simple interface makes it easy to add entries with one hand while being dragged along by over-enthusiastic puppies! The most recent release addressed the only two things I didn\'t like about the app.', "The app is exactly what I look for to keep track of my pet's daily tasks. It has a simple interface that its easy to use. I can easily add more custom items according to my dog's needs. N easily edit items by pushing the task to left. I do like them to record it in current time, so i can calculate walk time, by tapping walk at the start n grooming(cleaning) at the end of the walk. I really hope the data in the app can extracted in later version so it can be presented in doctor's visit. Thanks!", 'Great app for tracking a new puppy\'s every move. So easy to track food, weight, bowel movements, training etc. I love the option to add a photo and "like" or comment on everything. Also easily customize your own buttons (for example, we added "rest" in addition to the "nap" option). Overall great app that we are using as a "pack" with other family members who also have a new puppy.', 'This app used to be perfect. All I needed it was to log food walks and bathroom breaks. However, since my initial download several months ago they have broken every aspect of this. It has gotten to the point where I literally cannot open a dog. I have downgraded to a version of the app from 2018 and have zero issues. I have been sending crash logs regularly in hopes that they fix these problems to no avail. I will be happy to fix my rating once stability is back. Edit 11/4/19: The update to 3.8.13 has certainly fixed my stability issues but it has introduced a new problem. On the previous versions that I was using, when logging something a popup overlay would appear in the center of the screen to select the dog and write any notes. However, now it shows a redesigned full screen page. While I do like the aesthetics of this new page, it now places the dog selection and finish button at the two farthest points from your hand, at the top. With a majority of phone screens exceeding 5.5 inches this makes maintaining the leash complex. A remedy for this could be rearranging the icons to be at the bottom and placing the add a photo button at the top considering that most stabilize photos with two hands making the reach less bothersome.', "This app is the perfect thing that we were looking for. You can create custom recurring events as buttons to reuse. We created ones for sleeping, napping, and crate time. It's really the perfect solution for tracking your dogs habits. Especially great for learning a new puppy's time between eating and eliminating, and bladder control. Thank you for creating this!", 'Been using this app for a year, since shortly after we adopted our first cat and love it! Pretty easy to learn how it works, no obtrusive ads, and a great system for sharing access to the whole family. The only thing that could make it better to me would be the ability to hide certain actions from the "Log Events" screen because I don\'t plan to use some of them for kitty, such as "water" and "pee".', "Update 1/17/23 - Suddenly cannot use the app; it won't open, despite uninsta/reinstall. :( Really like being able to log when she went potty, when she ate, etc - very helpwful if you have ADHD! I also track when we train, go for a walk, any health issues that concern me (e.g. scratching a lot), and when she takes meds. I do wish there were more icons or you could add your own, because I have to repeat them a lot for what I track because there are so few and a limited variety.", "Good but offline issues - If you're out of the house without the internet & switch to a different app, when it goes to reload, it won't, and then when you get back home again & connect to the internet, all the information you added when out the house disappears. Just lost all the walk, pee, poop, drink, eating, treats, vet appointment logs etc I made when I was out. It's very annoying. It could at least store information on my phone to sync up later if I'm offline. I subscribe too.", "Responsive developer. Definitely the best app available. I'm looking forward to the updates. Currently, no ability to enter time of events at initial entry. The log is confusing to read; maybe use the pet photos on the log also? Currently everything looks the same. My Swype keyboard does not work in the app. Maybe allow for a neutral note entry in the log. To keep track of weird occurrences in the pup's life.", "This app has been very helpful to us logging three animals activities between 4 caregivers.  It's simple to use.  My only issue thus far is that when I log an activity it auto-selects every pet, and I have to unselect all, then just select one pet.  I can see where this could be handy for larger packs that do things together. However, I would love the option to set a 'default' selection - I do most activities with just one pet at a time.  Having a preset, or having none selected to start, would save me a couple steps each time.", 'I really love this app. I always end up with orphaned kittens that people bring me, and I often do the record-keeping on paper. This is even smarter. There are options for potty going and feeding. I do wish there was a way to keep records about temperature and body weight and the option to have records for cats as well as dogs. Also, a widget of some of the info would be awesome, too. Over all, it mostly filled the requirement I need in a tracking app.', 'This app allows me to customize events as well as reminders in addition to other already programmed preset options for me and gives a lot of freedom in regards to how many events and reminders you can log at a single time. When I had a question, after emailing, I recieved an answer to my question within half an hour. I may have personally needed help but I would say this app is user friendly and simple to navigate. Very happy with it.', 'Needs a lot of work. Can\'t edit/delete a record once you submit it. Can\'t mark an accident. Have to manually enter the start time twice. No "now" button for the end time to use it like a stopwatch; you instead have to manually input the end time. Default units are arbitrary. (e.g. for "poop" it defaults to a quantity of "miles") Back button on my phone always takes me to the dog chooser screen instead of screen I was previously on. Lack of stopwatch functionality is a deal-breaker for me', 'Was charged for the trial of the premium version. Unsubscribed immediately. Have emailed the developer asking for the money to be refunded. Waiting for a response.', "It's such a brilliant app for keeping records of everything about you dog, especially useful if they are regularly poorly so you can easily track records.", "Easy to add events. Would be better if you could set the time when you're adding an event, instead of having to edit it afterwards. Super for multiple people, nice notification when someone else logs an event. Statistics aren't great. I'd like to be able to visualise the time of day she's going to the toilet, and also in relation to feed time. Would be nice if the information could be exported to csv.", 'It\'s not a bad app, but it\'s crashing all the time for me. I can\'t log anything - I need to try at least 3 times before I\'m able to log anything without the app crashing on me. Also I don\'t understand why they stopped showing the weight history that we had since day 1 of us getting a puppy. For a couple of weeks it started showing only the latest logged wright event, but now it says "No events" logged - it\'s very upsetting :( I have the latest version of the app, but it still doesn\'t work.', "It's good but the only downside is there doesn't seem to be an undo button would be a nice feature. EDIT - There is a way to delete! Thankyou support team that makes the app so much easier to use! 10/10! Really useful for keeping track of toilet training and I love the fact you can add other activities 👌 would absolutely reccomend this to my friends with pets particularly puppies", "Great app, but there is no way to edit the log entries. I made some mistakes and also want to switch the way I document the heats, but I cannot go back and edit the old entries. I would make new ones but then I would have the entry doubled, since I can't delete the old ones. I like the possibility of creating custom log categories.", 'Edit: Thanks for responding! I updated my rating. Looking forward to the new version :) . . . I wish you could delete events, edit events, and add more than three pets (I use it for my ferrets too). I also wish there was a "vet" option. Other than that, it serves its purpose and we\'re able to communicate when we bring her out and feed her with everyone in our household.', "This app is AMAZING. A few small QOL things, but completely offset by how helpful it is. I'm tracking so many things for my cat who has some issues I need to keep an eye on, and this is MUCH easier than notepad. But...... Huge banner ad appeared at the top of the app today. It's very obnoxious. Still very worth it, and I 100% support them getting some income for it. I donated through the link. But maybe if you're going to go the ad route, you could have a paid ad free version? Still 5*, but 🤞?", "Update: They fixed the crashing issue really fast! I love this app because its really easy to log what you need to. It has a lot of features to use. However my main reason for getting an app like this is to be able to predict what time my dog will go potty. I was hoping the app would do this for me, but you have to pay $40 a year for it! I can't spend that much a year. I get that the makers of this app need money too, but I wish they would let you buy individual features without a monthly cost.", "I really like this app so far. The only thing I'm not happy with is in the profile feed. There are some fields like breed and food brand that I would like to add for my pup, but you seem to have to select from a dropdown. Having a rescue mix, my breed is not on there and my food brand also doesn't appear in the list. I would like the option to either select Mix or Other. Otherwise a freetext input field would be much more useful.", "Though not a dog owner, this app is the best I've found so far for tracking feeding and other necessary reminders for caring for our cats. I would love to see this expanded to include other animal breeds!!! My only downfalls, again not a dog owner but a pet owner who needs to keep track of pet health, are that some of the profile details don't have the option to be written in (food, breed, etc.). Also, I would like to be able to delete some of the activities that I do not use (i.e. outdoor activities). Again, this app would be PERFECT if it included other animal types as well!", "This app has helped me so much with tracking everything my new puppy. It had made potty training so much easier! One of the best free apps I've tried!", "Exactly what we needed for our new puppy. Especially if one person is taking over responsibilities during the night, morning, work hours, etc., we can easily see what happened and when to anticipate the upcoming events.The only thing we wish we could figure out is how to share reminders with the whole pack. Right now it looks like it's only visable to the person creating the reminders, but we are using this feature to set upcoming vaccinations, etc. and want the whole pack to get the reminders.", 'Briefly, overall, it gets the job done. But important things just arent options. We play ALOT more then we walk but there is no button for, "play". Each picture needs to be really small which sucks. I take many pics that I cannot send. There\'s no place in the feed to write a simple written update. I have to send 2 long texts during the day to give a more detailed update. The caption with each activity has to be under 7ish words. I could write a lot more. Definitely could be better IMO...', "It's a nice app with a clean interface. I like being able to track things about my puppy's health. However, the biggest downside to me is that I can't seem to find a way to edit or delete log entries. I wanted to add notes to a log after I made it, but I haven't found a way to edit it and I can't delete it and recreate the log with notes. This seems like a major feature that is completely missing. No options to work around this defect as far as I can tell."]

title: WBYF: Dating For Dogs
description:
WBYF (Wanna Be Your Friend) is the official International dating app for dogs. Join us and be part of a happy dog family.
Start connecting with other dog-lovers in your or any location to match, chat - swap pet photos and go on dates. 

MAIN FEATURES
- Profile for your dog
- Meet dogs near you or around the world
- Private messages
- Vote for your favourite dogs
- Today's Birthdays list
- Find puppies and dogs for sale online
- View Lost and Found dogs
- See if anyone else has liked your profile
- Memory page of dogs (This page is "In memory of beloved pets who went to heaven")
- Go on dog dates

FREE TO USE
WBYF is free to download and use.

CREATE YOUR ACCOUNT
Creating an account is easy! Enter a full date of birth and sex of your dog, then start filling in some basic information to create your profile.
summary: Find friends for your dog around you or from around the world

title: It's a Dog's Love: Romance you
description:
❏Synopsis❏

You expect your new job at Heaven, a famous pet store in Tokyo, will be pretty straightforward -- until you discover your handsome co-workers are actually half-dogs with the ability to transform at will! Dobe, Shephe, and Bernar entrust their secret to you, and you soon find family in the pack at Heaven… but not all is peaceful. When a rival pet shop sends thugs to destroy the store, you’re forced to stand your ground and defend your new home alongside your friends. 

Can you save the shop and find romance along the way? Find out in It’s a Dog’s Love!

❏Characters❏

◇The Withdrawn Doberman - Dobe◇
Aloof and alert, Dobe is the owner and leader of the pack at Heaven. Though initially cool and difficult to read, as you grow closer, you learn of a tragic event that continues to gnaw at his mind. Will you be able to resolve his past and help him trust again?

◇The Cocky German Shepherd - Shephe◇
Shephe may be a little boastful and self-centered, but he’s fiercely protective of his loved ones and won't go easy on anyone who attempts to harm them. Despite his impressive fighting ability, he harbors some self-doubt and wants to prove himself to you. Will he be the one that captures your heart?

◇The Innocent St. Bernard - Bernar◇
Bernar is the little brother of the pack at Heaven. Inquisitive and puppy-like, he adores humans and always sees the best in others — especially you! As you work together, he struggles with his newfound feelings of love. Will you show him what it means to be human?
summary: Experience a heartwarming romance with woman's best friend!
developerAddress: Stout Building 4th floor, 3-23, Kandasakumacho, Chiyoda-ku, Tokyo

comments: ['I\'ve played a dang good amount of these stories. Majority are hits and still somehow have somewhat different plot setups which is refreshing. I really loved the playfulness of this one and I loved it, up until the climax of the plot (before you pick your partner). That felt rushed to me, for some reason. However, I loved the change in the end where you get to pick your comfort level with the guy you picked. Like if you wanted to go all the way that night or "go slow", you decided. ❤️', "It's great, very cute story and easy to follow, I personally enjoyed it but I didn't really like the little mini game to earn points, most of the time it only gives my 2 points and it doesn't go any higher than that, the mini game also tends to get boring, I would suggest to put one or two more mini games to make it more fun, other than that I think this app is great :)", 'I really loved the story and the plot! It was just that it upset me knowing that i was out of tickets to get to the next story. Diamonds are easy to get, comparing to other similar games.I really apprecciate the time and effort that the creators/developers put into this game! I really recommend it if you are looking for a love story!', "The storyline and characters are great!!! The only problem I have is that we cant play minigames in between episodes and when we need to make choices. It's a little annoying having to stop the story to play the minigame but other than that, everything is perfect!", "I literally love this but more choices leading up to different routes would be good too , and if you create a point system about the main character's past choices or w/ other characters would be good. I would recommend that. Mostly just more choices to choose from that aren't charging rubies:) overall great app", "Omg, this game is INTENSE! And so are the boys (mainly Dobe) I really hated the fact that I have to wait 4 hours to get points or play one mini-game 100 times (more or less). Also, I'm kinda disappointed over the fact that you can't design your character besides the name. Overall though, I really enjoyed it.", 'I liked the story. the graphics are good. And i really enjoyed it. The reason i didnt put 5 star is bc 1. It was slightly fast paced with there meeting and such. its all based over a few months the first month passing fast. 2. the most important one is the rubies. BE PREPARED TO EITHER SPEND MONEY OR LOTS OF TIME! I didnt take two stars away be they do give u a trading system to get rubies and tickets for apps and actions. But very pricey and each choice is around 25 rubies. I did trade system.', "Love the different options available. My only problem was the spinning for coins. The option for choosing to watch a video is always no videos available. What an inconvenience! If u don't want ur gamers to watch the video then don't put the choice up...", "I love this game! The only thing is that the rubies are so expensive to get if you run out,and the mini game isn't that good either, for example, if you have 3 green hearts that aren't in a line you should still win some ponts but over that the game is awseome. I highly reccomend it with other Genius inc. Games.", "I've played a lot of apps by this company, and this one is probably my least favorite so far. Totally putting aside art, there was no time to actually bond with the characters. This one was really short compared to others I've played, and while I usually do get attached to characters, these guys felt like buddies or siblings, definitely not partners/potential partners.", 'Its not worth it. Frequent ad popups randomly when navigating menus. You can either pay money for Rubies in order to get the premium scenes, or earn points by watching an ad once every 4 hours, or getting lucky in a slot machine game and watch more ads to triple the point payout. You can then exchange points for rubies. The price for rubies is steep. I tried to dismiss the "buy rubies" menu but accidentally bought some without meaning too. I was charged a $35 dollar overdraft because of it.', 'I am just so in love with this app! Cute, adorable dogs, hot guys with the nicest and unique personalites in one and there are 3 of them! Like I mean I cant think of a better app, for real!! 😍😍 Not to mention the choices they give are resonable, unlike many similer apps and the story line is great too. The app is easy to use and not overly complicated. I was literally blushing the whole time❤❤❤❤ love this app!', "This game is soo fun. I absolutely love it and I'm so addicted to it but I only have two complains. 1: why are gems so expensive 😭😭😭 please give us a way to earn them or something. 2: can't you make the ticket wait a little shorter please 🙄🙄. But at the end of the day really great game I highly recommend it to anyone, especially people with unlimited data and some money. 😂😂😁", "There are no technical issues, very few grammer mistakes but I can't help but feel the storylines and the love interests have a repitive pattern. It feels like playing the same thing over and over again. You need to explore different personalities for both MC and love interests and you need to come up with unique storylines.", "I love this game and I'm not even done playing through it. The characters are all so handsome and sweet and they never fail to surprise me with new parts of their personality. When Bernar said he loved me, I literally erupted in giggles. When Shephe was about to kiss me, I wished so bad that Dobe hadn't walked in. Honestly, I think the game is amazing, and the only thing that really bothers me is the pay-to-play choices.", 'I so love dogs and this app was so cute, however i hate having to reject any of them, they are all cute and but each romantic choice costs so much and every ruby cost so many points, i will have to play hours before i can purchase enough rubies for a free scene, i got one free love scene with just an ad at the beginning chapter but after that, its pay for it. I might reinstall later but i have another yaoi app of yours that i want to finish, please lower your prices so i can enjoy more games.', 'Its great! I love it and the story. I gave it three stars because of the gems, sometimes you end up saying something a bit rude or weird because you dont have enough gems. also the minigame! please add another one ^^ it gets a bit boring after a while overall, its a nice, sure the gems bother me a bit, but i like it!', "I love this game so much. They are all adorable, but it's stupid when I want to earn points to exchange for diamonds. I downloaded 2 games to download and run and it said it would give me 30 or 40 points and then it said we don't have this on the list anymore! So I have to pay for it instead of exchanging!! I hate it! Other than that it's a good game", 'Good game, super cute, and i love it! But the only thing is, ive been playing it for a while. But recently, it wont let me back in and keeps on saying something went wrong everytime i go on it. If you fix this i think MY expirience for the game would be better. But beside that, its a really good game, almost perfect!', "I love the storyline, and the guys(particularly Shephe XD), but... two stars because of the gems, and how you're restricted on what to say. Sometimes, you can answer kinda rudely, but if you really really like that person, and don't have enough gems, there's just no feel for the story! Please please please make the gems no more! Or at least refill the gems everyday or something. All I want is to enjoy a good story, and you're giving me one: but you're also taking all the fun out of it!", "I really like this game. It's a good story to follow along with. You don't get many gems or tickets but I think it's worth the wait. I found out I could divide my time to play it in the morning, the middle of the day, and at night so I could get more tickets and watch ads to get more coins for gems. I definitely recommend it, even my friend likes it", 'I love the story it\'s taken me more than 6 months of watching videos and playing the mini game once a day but I loved this app only reason I\'m uninstalling it is because I finished all routes and endings. More than 6 months I grinding up points but I got all those "paid" for options took a lot of patience', 'I love the whole story! Honestly i think that bennar was the cutest (dont hate me!). Though i wish we could have more ways to earn the dimonds to do the questions that require that. Please make it to where we can use our coins that you can earn i think that would make the game even better! I love the way the game makes you feel like your attcualy making contact and talking to the charictors!! I highly recomend the game!!!! Over all one of my favorte games!', "Adorable and cute!💕 The fact that you have me simping over all 3 of them. My only complaint is you have to use a slot machine to get only 2 and 4 coins, also I can't watch videos to multiply by 3. But I don't really care, it's still awesome and I totally recommend this game! 😊", "I've only started playing this and i'm enjoying it already.They all have unique personalities which i'm fascinated of...my only problem is about the gems,why do they cost that much? and it literally makes you wait 2 hours and so on to refill the story tickets but so much for that,I still love the game and i'm looking forward for more of it.", "I LOVE THIS GAME!! I love the characters,the different choices,and how you can have a romance route with all of them without choosing I'm also playing immortal heart I've became a fan of that game and wanted to download and play more of your games I've also downloaded my mystic dragons I'm a fan of ur company now! Keep up the good work and for those of u reading this, you will not be disappointed only the fact u have to save up rubies and wait 2 hrs for 2 tickets but it's worth it!best game evr", 'The game is outstanding...good visuals,storyline and choices but i gotta admit it was a bit frustrating that the premium choices literally takes up all the diamonds and its hard to get it back....', 'So I love this game the stories are addicting! But the thing is I want there to be another way to get tickets other than buying them because I dont spend money on online games and the thing is, I was only able to watch 3 episodes with the 3 tickets and It makes me very sad that I cant watch more episodes, Please fix it please.', "The storyline was amazing! I really hated wasting my gems tho since it's really hard to get gems in the game when you spend them but overall i really liked the plot of the story and the twist in the end! I hope to see more stories like these in the end! :D", "I am absolutely hooked to your games like this, but i have a suggestion, i noticed all of the characters are so pale skinned, would you be willing to add some color to their features besides their hair? In starlit proposes, the one with purple hair (i forgot his name) he's actually tanned.... I just thought you needed more like that. Other then that, I'm good.", "I love the theme song! I was skeptical but Im glad I tried it. Never knew lowkey beastiality could be this sweet. Reminded me a lot of 'Heart of Fox'. The only issue I had with the game was that the story was hastily done in the end. Why were the delinquents vandalizing the shop? What happened to the rival shop? Also I was sure than Cain had something to with it since he was the only one who knew we were out, that route would've slapped. Hes involved. Theres tension. Build up. We bust him. Boom.", 'The graphics are alright. The storyline is random but still makes a little sense. Although, the "good" choices are around 20 diamonds and story tickets are low. All of their other games has these diamonds system.', 'It\'s a super nice game I like this game more than "Loyalty for love: Romance you choose" and "Destined Memories : Romance Otome Game" but too shame that the ending is the same 😐 SHORTTTTTTTT😑. I mean COME ON! Please make it more romantic and happy for us two😭. If you guys r unsure to play this than give it a try tho that\'s it.', "i never write reviews but i loved this story so much.. i love everything the soundtrack, the characters, the story feels so warm cute and sweet. i cried a lot with the dobe and gabriel story :( but what i love most of all ARE THE CHARACTERS. i am so in love with this story definitely one of the best i've ever read i wish there were more like this. maybe a 2nd season?? ❤️", 'I absolutely loved this game I love these kinds of games and I got all of the romance endings! I do wish they had like sum games to be able to refill the tickets faster but other wise loved it!!!', "its just a MASTERPIECE no words but a m a z i n g, Genius inc games are always fun to play! its 100% worth a try! i reccomend u to at least try it :3 u wont regret it! besides u wont believe how many of these i play O-O''' as always the problem with da rubbies well its easy peasy for me with no payment-in card-real money thingy- i dont mind spending some hours to earn it :D its worth ur time im 100% sure! dont turn this game down", "Its anamazing app,great detail and the characters are really cute. I dont have any problems or lags, i love this game to. I'd give this rate 5 because it makes me energatic and it always makes me blush. This game is on piont", "I love this game, I've also realised that Dobe and Bernar literally share my personality, so yeah, I love this game, it's one of my favourite games of all time, you have mad it really hard for me to chose between Dobe and Bernar though, but I love a challenge in a relationship,or even just picking one", "The main issue for me is that some of the LIs look underage. If the player is underage, there is no issue. For those players who aren't underage, there is only one LI to choose from. That is just my personal, subjective opinion. Although the plot is lacking entertainment value, as an advocate for animals, I did appreciate the awareness and information game brought to the proper treatment and value of the lives, emotional well-being and safety of our furry friends.", 'I really love this game 💖 but there is just one problem that sometimes it takes rubies to Answer any questions. But still love this game and lot. And the person whom I like the most is Berner😊💖💗in this game. He is so cute and Adorable. 💗💖. Thanks for designing this game. I really enjoyed it.']

title: Dog Town: Puppy Pet Shop Games
description:
Start your own Dog Town by breeding and collecting dogs. Experience dogs training where your puppies can learn lots of new commands. Train your dog & puppy, send them to quests and funny adventures. Raise your animals and take care of cute puppies in Dog Town simulator games! Pet your puppy, wash, groom, feed like in real life! Enjoy the cute puppy town with unique pet story & training feature. You can get new dog & puppy cards from pet store for your puppy town & collect them. Discover doggy games and customize the rooms where your dogs live! Design your own interiors with hundreds of decorations that you can find in game virtual store. 
 
In Dog Town you can:
 
★ Train your dogs and teach them lots of tricks with new training feature!
★ Breed and Collect new dogs! 
★ Enjoy gorgeous 3D environment! 
★ Play with realistic Dogs with lifelike behavior!
★ Take care of your dogs: brush, wash, train, pet & feed!
★ Level up your dogs and send them to quests!
★ Decorate your rooms with hundreds of decorations! 
★ Collect more than 100 dogs and more with each update!
 
If you always wanted to adopt pets or any animal, play with puppies and dogs & were interested in animal shelter, pet & puppy rescue then this is one of the best virtual games for you. Grow your littlest doggo and have fun grooming them . Each animal has a unique character and behavior, so you will always recognize your "Sleepy" from the "Jumpy"! Also you will see their unique behavior while training your puppy. We've put a tremendous amount of effort to ensure that you would feel attached to your animal dogs just like you would to the real ones.
 
In this dog & animal simulation game you can collect dog breeds like: Basset hound, Staffordshire Bull Terrier, Springer Spaniel, Boston Terrier, Labrador Retriever, Australian Shepherd, German Shepherd, Yorkshire Terrier, Bull Terrier, Great Dane, Schnauzer, Cocker Spaniel, French Bulldog, Pomeranian, Doberman, Siberian Husky, Miniature Pinscher, Beagle, Chihuahua, Corgi, Dachshund and other dog breeds. After training your puppies they will become stronger & will participate in more challenging quests. There is a large emphasis on Dog Collection and management for casual and midcore players. 
 
Download now and start having fun with cute pets!
 
 
Enjoyed Dog Town? Join our community:
https://www.facebook.com/groups/382045606113476
 
Please note! This game is free to play, but it contains items that can be purchased for real money. If you are having any problems in the game or have a great idea about it please contact gamesupport@frismos.com
