comments: ["The app is good. But it's too costly. A month subscription should not be more than #2,000 at the highest. It's not like someone is watching Netflix or Prime on the app. Why does it have to be so costly. Fix the prize or you're going to lose most customers. Also, the 6 months offer for #9,000 came up and I was going to get that, but I can't find it anymore. But, even if I subscribe, the people I chat won't be able to reply since they are not on premium so it's pointless", "If I could vote zero star I will do that. This app is totally fake, having fake profiles, no people in my area, you can't simply text or reply anyone without subscription, whenever you open app you start receiving random texts from random profiles to makd you busy in app. Its all fraud. Do not download it.", "Functionality was fine, accuracies in profiles is highly questionable. Huge amount of fake profiles, both picture-wise and demographically. How can a few dozen individuals like a profile when there is no picture or information in the profile, doesn't make sense. My mistake, should have saved the $$.", 'None of the filters work, and no way to know if the people are near you or not. Ok to use free, but would not recommend subscribing until features are fixed', "Basically what everyone else is saying on here. I'm 100% on board with an app that makes women actually do SOMETHING when it comes to dating, but this is nothing but a bunch of bots trying to get you to spend money. Fake accounts, fake profiles, just don't even bother. Will be refunding.", "Too many fake profiles. You have to pay for everything separately! The separate costs are unnecessary. It's expensive over here.. I can't even know which area the people are in by default. Each tab takes too long to load each time, I do not like this setup.", "I have a paid subscription and if theirs not enough people in your city it does people from thousands of miles away and other countries was told to raise or lower age limit and basically isn't what some people are looking for in meeting possible friends or relationship. Not a good app very disappointed", "The idea and concept of the app is cool. None of the filters work when you're looking through profiles it doesn't even show people in your same city profiles of people all over the country hundreds of miles away and it asks to be verified and when you put a picture on there to try to be verified it doesn't accept your picture. It would be a nice app if it actually worked", "So many fake profiles. I didn't have a profile for 2 seconds before someone liked me and sent a message... that you can't reply to without paying. Haven't had the app but 10-12 hours and of the 21 messages... 4 are now inactive users. Don't waste your time... or at least money.", 'Imma quote something they say but it\'s actually false "The site allows you to meet new people nearby and make new friends online for free. So you can chat and connect with comfort and ease" cause in fact you can\'t chat with people unless you pay and get the subscription for it to be able to chat', "Automatic fake messages right from the start and even a simple texting is paywalled by premium. In normal world Kismia won't be in the app store, but in the jail. The worst part is their bot-review and meaningless answers to complaints when in reality you get a reation from other user even before you finish the signing up. And, yeah, you can't even answer these bots without premium account. It is truly a clown world.", 'The app showed immediate bad intention$ right frm the beginning. A lot of "women" or probably bots, messaged me immediately but you can\'t message them back without going premium. There\'s not even a single day free trial!? App used for 10 minutes only and I\'m removing it now', "after spending 24 hours with the app I can confirm that most profiles are fake and I can only guess set up by the developers to make it more appealing, it's simple do a reverse image search the profiles come up on various places with different names different locations etc, I even had a fake female account set up and guess what it was matching with people by itself 😂 avoid this app it's a scam (edit) the developers come out with the same response to everyone that slates the app haha try again", 'Nothing without premium, and premium/gold is very expensive (That\'s why almost no one can write to you, and even if you have the membership, others don\'t get your messages and they can\'t answer you well). It doesn\'t let you post photos you like unless they\'re in the order the app wants, and you don\'t have the option to put your Instagram ID or phone number. It also has a "smart messages" system (it sends you different phrases or questions as opposed to what the other person sees).', "Absolutely wasting of my time. You can't reply to messages people sent you. You have to have premium. Or they have to have it. Why would I pay for this if I don't know whether those people are real or fake? The concept is a total garbage. I'm not going to pay for texting. Are you going to charge for the amount of symbols used in a message as well?", 'Beware!!! Total scam! Save your money! I would give zero stars if i could... Almost 100% fake-profiles. (Got around 10 real contacts over 1 month, all across the world, nothing within my region. App says "less then 100km away from me, asked her ... Almost 5000km away!) Automated messages, over night you always get around 7-10 likes. To evaluate this i liked all (!!!) other profiles/matches and one would expect an increase of likes/messages. But it stays exactly the same.', "Worst dating site, everyone in this app are mostly not real, almost all verified account are fake person, Please the developers should know how to solve this problem, a verified account yet it will be fake person, how can someone be using a verified account yet it won't be the original person, I've chat with lots of verified account there but all fake. Please guys, don't download it, and don't pay for anything. Let Kismia upgrade their security check. Nonsense app. And they don't even believe", 'Very very useless application. I subscribed for one week 3700 + they deducted that and still deducted another 3000 + from my acct. my money was deducted twice and no value for d money deducted. Just sending Friendship messages without any Friendship connection nd response. Very Useless', "very easy to navigate there were a few challenges which unfortunately outweighed my overall experience I'll just ride out the end of my present subscription and see what happens from there", "Another scam app. They advertise you can message for free but that's a lie, you need to upgrade to message anyone even after matching. Fake profiles and a complete scam.", "It was under absolutely free dating apps and it's not absolutely free. You have to pay to see if they like you and to send messages deleting it right away", "You said there is a search where you can search for people in your location but there is nothing of such cuz I just try looking for search icon or whatever but there wasn't A complain is made for you to improve the app not for you to make or give the same respond to every review and the issue is still not fixed. How can I be given a location that is not even close to where am staying how ? I don't even know this place like some thousand miles away from my location. Work on it please .", "The app is very useless and seems unreal. Fake profile and fake messages just to get someone subscribed to their scam. Don't even bother downloading or installing the app if you haven't. Total waste of resources and time.", "The only thing this app offers is free registration. Once that happens, you'll get the fake bots to try to lure you in to chat with someone. But you can't chat cause you gotta pay to use the service. It's pretty much a scam app. Since there's no way of knowing, you'll be getting what you pay for. It's nothing more than a basic dating app with the same concept as the rest. But if you wanna risk it, then try it. It will cost you.", 'The app is unusable without paying. I would never pay before experiencing the real account population, but it doesn\'t give you that chance. Reply: How about you instead make the app useable without paying, most other success datings apps are describ as "useable" atleast.', "This app is absolutely garbage. Typical of the Internet dating age we're experiencing! Charging men to send messages to obviously fake profiles. Women sending automated messages without conversation! I would NOT recommend this app to a dog! Complete waste of time and Money. Better off using your hand fellas", "It's obvious, these sites were not designed to have anyone meet in person. The use of fictional entertainers is appealing. When you think, fake profiles, it can be true, because those in the photos are not who anyone is speaking with, yet it sucks when you pour out your heart when life kicks you down. To me, this is a version of stealing someone's money all for a show. I'd be better to watch porn, it's fake in itself, yet if you wanted to watch the videos. I'm here to meet real women, not fake.", "Edit after reply: -- Exactly as you say; REGISTERED users are real, not all of them. It's just plain bullsh*t. -- FAKE AND SCAM! I have never experienced on dating apps that within moments of installing you are flooded with messages of so many 'women'. This app does. I can only explain that it is a huge scam. You cannot even reply to these mesaages because you have to pay a quite large sum to do so. Do NOT waste your time, energy and certainly your money on this. Proper SCAM.", "Although it is filled with scammers and people with a business agenda, I have chatted with a couple of real ladies. Be aware when asked to move to another app too soon! That's a red flag. The easiest way to know for sure, if you are or not in a chat with a scammer, is to ask them to do life video chats, once you are in another app. If they start with excuses, that is a red flag. If they do the life video chat, be aware that it is not just a short video with no sound. That's definitely a scammer!", "Waste of money.. too many fake profiles with fake certified photos.. you cannot send messages unless you pay.. I get alot of fake messages with phrases that nobody really uses in real life.. I bought the weekly package and I haven't received 1 authentic message. I have 8 photos up but it's pointless.. Nobody is ever online, if I type in new York City it only shows 1 or 2 ladies profile.. give me a break.. these are money grab sites for women looking for rich guys", "the app is second to none as far as dating is concerned,,, your comments are received and replied to instantly by people who are interested in you ,,, keep it up kismia,,,,,,,,,,,, although I have not been able to find/ date any Lady here .this is due to your payment process,,, can it be as flexible as Facebook,,,if you have data you can access fotos , video ,infact almost anything but if you don't have data you will only have access to very few features", 'is a nice app, but the monetary charges is much, you dont have to say subscribe for everything its makes the app boring, I dont know how much you are paying for the servicing of the app, but and readjust to with prices so as to make it more fun like other social apps. its will make you to go far beyond your expectations.', 'Unfulfilling. Very disapointed. Can not do anything but like profiles have to upgrade for eveything else. So if you got 20 bucks for a wk it might be worth it. Oh women message you first but nonr answer back if you can respond.', "Blocked before I finished making my account and I didn't break any of thier guidelines and now I can't even delete my account because I can't view my profile to open the settings to delete it, contacted the customer support and they were useless asking me to access an account they had blocked me from accessing so I could contact them through the account, the one that I can't get into because they blocked it absolutely stupid waste of time.", 'It said I could chat for free. I was able to reply to one person, but for two other people, it said "reply not sent" and prompted me to sign up for premium in order to message people back.', "Can't chat with the obviously fake profiles on this app without paying money upfront. Give me an ad option or stop making bot profiles to trick men into thinking there are women on the app. Women don't message first on any dating app including bumble.", "This app is rubbish they will renew the subscription without your permission and they will ask you to pay for literally everything. You will have to pay to see people that liked your pic you will also pay for your profile to get verified couple with they will renew the subscription without your permission this app sucks I don't advise anyone to download this app", "This is just filled with fake AI profiles . I just waited my 19.6 pounds. After one premium subscription, they will now tell you to get God premium sub. What a rubbish. Don't download this app please, make another reasonable thing with your hard earned money. Can you people refund me please, I am done like what I see after subscription.", 'Definitely a fake app, You will get fake messages and likes, to get you to buy the gold package, then all of a sudden those accounts that messaged you get deactivated lol, dont waste your time or money', "Like the rest of these apps, they are after one thing (your money) they don't care. They don't want you to match with anyone because 1 matched pair = 2 lost customers. Go back to the old way meet someone at a party or in a pub somewhere."]

title: Mamba Lite - dating & chat.
description:
Meet Mamba Lite - it's a free dating app and site! Download, swipe, meet new people, make friends, chat, flirt, date and love! All the functions of our app are designed to make it easier to find a company to chat with or a soulmate for the lifetime.
 
MAMBA LITE IS
✔ A big choice among the men and women registered on MAMBA LITE
✔ Many new connections every day.
✔ Mamba Lite is popular in 50+ countries of the world.
✔ At the moment, many users are online, one third of them are new. 
 
BENEFITS:
 
MAMBA Lite is a FREE and SAFE platform for dating and communication.
Technologies based on artificial intelligence automatically recognize and then block fake activity and users with inappropriate behavior. Our support service is ready to solve any issue 24/7.
 
QUICK REGISTRATION via social networks and by phone number.
Create a new account or register via Facebook. It takes you just 10 seconds before you can start dating!
 
SEARCH FOR PEOPLE NEAR YOU or in other locations!
✔ Meet and communicate with those who are nearby now.
✔ The app shows you the people you interact with during the day, such as in your work area and close to home.
✔ Or you can search for people in other cities and countries.
 
FILTERS
Set filters depending on what you expect from dating! Are you looking for friends, romance or light flirting, or maybe dates, love and serious relationships?
Use advanced filters by dating purpose. Communicate only with those with whom your goals coincide!
Do you want to make new acquaintances considering all your preferences?
Use filters by type, financial status, education, marital status, having children, or sexual preferences.
 
MATCHES
Do you want reciprocity? It's simple!
Go to the "Encounters" tab and Mamba Lite algorithms will select people especially for you. If you like the person, swipe right, if you want to move on, swipe left. When your likes match, you get a notification and can start chatting.
--
Not enough free features? Paid services will expand the functionality of the application!
✔ Boost up your profile and make it more popular among the users.
✔ Hide your account so that only selected users can see it.
✔ Send gifts to everyone you like, wish friends a happy birthday and congratulate them on other holidays.
--
Mamba Lite is a free dating app for single adults popular in many countries all over the world. Meet new people, make friends, use online chat and find love!
summary: Find a partner or friends, communicate, date and start a relationship!

title: Plinder- Dating. Chat. Meet
description:
With Plinder, it’s easy to be you. Easy to match your way, date your way. Meet new people your way. 💜

Welcome to free dating app, the airtripp dating app that makes it easier to date. We’re a little different from other free dating apps and dating sites.

Whether you’re hoping to find ‘the one’, lots of foreign friends or a number-one friend – we’ve got you covered.
Our free dating app gives you the tools to put yourself out there. The real, unfiltered you. So if you’re looking to meet new people and make new friends & chat international (online and irl), you can have confidence in the connection.
Put the joy back into online dating – download our free app today.


Perks of using our dating app:

🙆‍♀️ Your profile celebrates you, the real you
Easy to meet up with new people & meet local in your area
Can find something long-term, short-term or make friends!
Lots of ways to customise your profile
Inspires great chats and great dates
Can switch between message chats and chat international
Helps keep the spark going with long-distance relationships
Easily find friends in local dating with shared interests
Of course, LGBTQ+ friendly 🌈
Profiles can be checked out by your own approval committee (your pals on the app)
It’s fun, flirty – and, because you can’t put a price on that great-date feeling – free

Features to help you on your dating adventure:

Shared intentions let you know where you stand
‘chat foreign friends before you match’ lets you test the waters
Filters help finesse your search for a date with dating x & dating xp
Profile prompts help to get those chat-balls rolling
Highlighted interests make it easy to spot potential dates and find friends
Fun, in-chat games can break the ice before you meet first date
Connecting with Apple Music makes it easy to make friends!
chat international helps with getting to know people better (and quicker)
Here you can explore tamil2friends & ts dating also.


Perks of dating with Premium Plus:

⭐️ Boosts chances of meeting perfect matches
⭐️ Can send a crush to kick-start a flirty chat & hook up
⭐️ Reveals who’s already liked you
⭐️ Shows people who’ve added you to their favourites
⭐️Can undo your last ‘no’, if you change your mind
⭐️ Unlimited use of filters makes it easier to find friends  & meet foreign friends and great matches
⭐️ Gives your messages top-priority to get those chats going in airtripp dating app
⭐️ Can go incognito, if you’d like to limit who sees your profile
⭐️ No ads! So you’re free to date without distraction


How our free dating app helps to keep you safe:

💚 Our dating app has a one-stop shop for handy guides, tools & helplines - the 'Safety Space'
✅ Photo verification checks people are who they say they are
🥒 Private detector flags (and initially blurs) inappropriate pictures
🧌 Rude message detector protects – and empowers – you when chatting to strangers and online friends
🧑‍🎤 Selfie request helps you check people are still who they’ve said they are, before you meet up irl
❇️ Block, report, and unmatch gives you complete control of your dating journey


Diversity and inclusivity:

As we’re big believers in the importance of recognition, we’d like to make it super clear our free dating app is a safe space for all sexual orientations (lesbian, queer, gay-dating and all other kinds of dating), faith-based dating (Muslim, Jewish, Christian-dating...all beliefs) and all cultures. At Badoo, we welcome everyone.

----
Plinder is a dating app that is free to download and use. We also offer optional subscription packages and non-subscription, single, and multi-use paid features.
Your personal data is securely stored on Plinder - be sure to read our privacy policy and terms and conditions
https://plinderdating.com/privacy
https://plinderdating.com/terms

title: USA Dating
description:
Datee is using science to help you find your perfect match .. in seconds!
* If a man can’t decide what to wear on a date, he might want to wear blue. Studies show that women are attracted to men in blue.
* Women who post a photo receive twice as many messages as women who don’t.
* On average, it takes between 12 to 14 dates before couples will trade house keys.
* Couples usually wait until six to eight dates before they are willing to enter into an exclusive relationship.
* Close to 45% of dating members in the United States have children.
* 92% of single parents would rather date other single parents.
* There are 95.9 million unmarried people in the U.S. of which 47% are men and 53% are women.
* 4 out of 10 workplace dating relationships result in marriage.

We know a lot about dating. Let our science work for you. Let us help you find your perfect partner.

Honest, straightforward matches and contacts for singles and couples. 

Free messages, matches, likes, favorites, global chat, and video calls. 

A lot more inside.
summary: Scientifically designed matches. Find your perfect match in seconds!

comments: ['Its not good, after enter you email etc when u go for open its show your password is incorrect, its just time wasting app so please i request to all for not installing such type of rough app', 'The only problem is that one race is more superior to others i.e Philippines are shown much more as compared to other races...', "I don't know what's going on with this app, but I'm about to deactivate it if I do not get customer assistance within the next hour. It keeps telling me my location is off even when it's on so my location cannot be verified and I don't know if that's hindering me from sending messages because currently I am unable to respond to those who have mrssaged me.", 'Thought the bad reviews were a joke. They werent. This app doesnt allow you to delete your profile & doesnt allow you to post selfies you already have on your phone. It forces you to take one via your camera like right away. Why do that when I took better photos before? Not even the Website (Datee.mobi) allows it. It forces you to use the app instead just to upload a selfie. Also false advertising. This app is International, not for Americans. Nice going with that.', "Can't even get my damn profile up, app won't let me move on even though I fill in everything. Or it jumps back to a previous section and I have to fill that out again! I have tried bad dating apps before but this is the worst one yet! Uninstalling, don't waste your time!", "If there is anything more than 1 star that is what I could have rate this useless app. I mistakenly downloaded this useless app, opened an account with them. Now it telling me that I can't upload my profile photo from my phone's gallery. I tried to delete my account but the useless app doesn't have a deletion option. Please how can I delete my account?", "I had to subscribe so as to apload a picture since wasn't in a position to take a good selfie. After subscriptions and my $$10.21 gone, I can't login anymore. The App keeps taking me back to login, after successful login, it takes me back to filling the questionnaire......what a heck!!! I need my $10.21 back as soon as possible.you are Stealing people money", 'Yeah we can find dates but many problems are there with the app I gave the app location access but still it is showing error which is not the case with the site and I am not able to upload a photo from gallery whenever I click on the add photo button it directly opens the camera basic operations really suck here', "it's when l have started to look for matches so give time", "it's the best app ever I got alot of notification of women I only dream off.", "Why this app sucks: 1. No account delete option. If someone wants to remove their profile they should be able to. 2. To force people to take a selfie before they can complete the process is horrible. You cant even upload a picture and if you delete it it takes you back to that selfie page. 3. You cant select the range or age of who you want to contact. 4. Full of creepy people. If I was an admin I'd be checking the message board. I'm pretty sure there are pedophiles leaving messages.", 'Won\'t even allow for a photo already taken to be used in registration process, wants to charge $10 a month for such a "premium" feature. Obviously just another clickbait app, waste of time', "Can't find a girls on there 20-35, everytime I try changing browsing settings, the age thing won't work, the location is a joke, none of the girls are near me, I like the price, but this app is useless.", 'No way to delete profile. app is basic, no way to select preferences so it makes you look at everyone. Not my idea of a good way to meet someone. Serious waste of time', "Been using this for days with zero interaction. It's obviously mostly fake profiles & not even a good fakery algorithm; half the girls have guy's names, pix pulled from anywhere & patently not real. No filters, meaning I'm getting guys profiles & old grannies to choose from. Most other profiles are Russian or Filipino. Not a single profile within 200 miles of my location. & USA singles? haha... not had a single yank in 1,000s of swipes! Just don't bother. Oh, & intrusive ads all the time too!", "terrible interface and preferences are not saved. I don't want to be matched with 70 year old grandma's. fix or I will be deleting", 'Good app but the ads keep Disturbing me.', "Redirects you to another app. Doesn't allow photo upload. No matches in area, gives matches hundreds of miles away and those matches are very low quality.", 'havent been on long, but seems to be ok so far...only i cant do anything because it wont send an email for me to verify. ive tried 10 times, checked in spam and trash. even tried with two seperate emails. nothing.', "Seems really not necessarily slow and constantly saying to many user's online haven't been able to talk to anyone. Just a waste of time and space good thing I didn't spend any money on it.", "it says it's 100% free but isn't, to see location you have to subscribe to gold subscription, for people with not much money who want to use this app it will be totally useless to them , this app gives false information, I'm uninstalling and never returning until its 100% Free", "HORRIBLE You have to pay just to know a person's area, and even to add more photos you have to pay. No good. Good thing I didn't purchase a subscription.", 'The application has too many glitches, and needs to be fixed. I had to do numerous restarts to get it to work. Filtering on age ranges should be allowed for all users, not just the subscribers. Big fat joke!', "Needs options to filter locations . Also I've seen separate profiles using the same pic. Over all it doesn't look like anyone is even on here.", "Terrible app. Don't use. Full of disgusting people and it won't allow you to use the age filters. That SHOULD be a FREE function. I would rate this less than one star if I could. Also makes it impossible to delete your account.", "This site is full of scammers.. When I deleted my account the developers didn't care that someone (male) had taken my name and the messages that has been on my profile.. He changed the picture, and profile info but kept all messages...DONT GET ON THIS SITE... nothing but scams and if the developers aren't part of it they surely don't care..", 'How they even say is not full of scammers. A lot of fake accounts, a lot of fake pictures. And you need to pay 10$ to see the location. Really and is easy to catch the scammer because all the time they going to ask about your WhatsApp because they can see your phone number and after a robocaller is going to call you.', 'Im just new and just starting whats in here so far... I cauldnt validated the said email for yo be able to talk to someone. Ive been sending many times already but it didnt responsing it keeps saying i have expired email validation its tiring...', "Buggy and A VERY hard to understand App! PLUS, if you want to permanently delete your account from this App, there is no option to do so whatsoever. Don't waste your time and effort with this One.", "The app is good I love it but it seems there are fake people in it, apart of credit card you people can give another method of paying so that does of us who don't have credit card can pay with another method", "This is the worse app ever do not download it. I emailed them to find out how to delete it. Omg it's the worse no one close nor does anyone speak. So don't waste your time.", "Needs work on settings in town area's & profile age, miscellaneous.
